description: Nouveax HDPC Rigid Core Vinyl Tile Flooring couples the look of real tile with the exceptional performance only a rigid plastic composite core can deliver. These tiles are embossed to feel like real tile and offer a contemporary, bold, and beautiful style to your home or office. Perfect for high traffic areas, including kitchens, bathrooms and basements. The tiles are 100% waterproof and require no acclimation prior to installation. HDPC Rigid Core increased strength and density hides sub-floor imperfections, floats over most existing hard surface floors, and is perfect for the DIY homeowner. HDPC Rigid Core Vinyl Tile Flooring is combined with an attached foam pad that reduces sound transmission and increases comfort when walking. Nouveax HDPC Rigid Core Vinyl Tile Flooring is EPA (TSCA title VI) compliant and also has the coveted GreenGuard Gold certification, which provides safer and healthier indoor home and work environments. Waterproof peace of mind, the added benefit of a safer product, and Nouveax’s tough Urethane Ceramic finish provides the right flooring solution for active families or office spaces.

description: Need a floor ready to stand up to the toughest challenges. SMARTCORE Pro is the smart choice for the most demanding environments. Armed with commercial-grade durability for pro-level performance, SMARTCORE Pro is built with COREtec technology for a floor that works hard so you can play hard. With SMARTCORE Pro, you don't have to sacrifice style for strength. You get the look and feel of the real thing with the durability your space demands. Plus, it's 100% waterproof, easy to install, a breeze to clean and stays strong even in the hottest sunrooms or coldest cabins. Now that's beauty with muscle. When you want flooring designed for you and the demands of your life, there's a SMARTCORE for that.

description: Built on the belief that modern life needs modern solutions, GE Profile Appliances are designed to make daily life simpler by incorporating Smart Home technology and cutting-edge features in every appliance. GE Profile’s sleek design and quality engineering will give your kitchen the most up-to-date look and the best innovative performance you’ve been looking for.
descriptionHtml: Built on the belief that modern life needs modern solutions, GE Profile Appliances are designed to make daily life simpler by incorporating Smart Home technology and cutting-edge features in every appliance. GE Profile’s sleek design and quality engineering will give your kitchen the most up-to-date look and the best innovative performance you’ve been looking for.
features: Power Boil on Two Tri-Ring Elements - This cooktop has 3,600 and 3,000 tri-ring elements that allow for different pan sizes to be used for rapid boiling,Precision Temperature Control - set your burner to an exact degree, not just high, medium or low, using a smart pan, the cooktop maintains a specific temperature – from 100 to 500 degrees; perfect for sauces, candies and frying,Guided Cooking - connect a smart pan to your cooktop and your burners will adjust time and temperature based on a video-guided recipe in the app; choose from thousands of recipes and get perfectly cooked food (Pan sold separately),Glide Touch Controls - choose from 11 different heat settings with one easy swipe for total heat control,Easy Clean Surface - a smooth glass surface and glide touch controls makes cleaning up messes simpler than ever on this easy clean electric cooktop,Smart Cookware Rebate - smart pans and a wireless sous vide probe easily pair with this smart cooktop to ensure you get the perfect cooking results; earn a rebate for a free 11-in Hestan Cue Smart Pan,Built-in WiFi - this smart cooktop features Built-In WiFi so you can monitor your burners and view power levels, precision temperature, or on/off,Synchronized Elements - connect and control two cooktop burners as one to create a bigger cooking surface for pans such as griddles,Synchronized Fan and Lights - synchronize your cooktop and GE Profile over-the-range microwave or hood so that your fan or hood and lights automatically come on when a burner is activated with Chef Connect
name: GE Profile 36-in 5 Burners Smooth Surface (Radiant) Black Smart Electric Cooktop

Our vinyl tile offers long lasting, rigid core flooring ready for your active household. Our ACTIVELIFE SHIELD™ provides the dent, abrasion, and scratch resistance that busy homes demand. It’s waterproof, stain-resistant, and easy to clean so everyday accidents are not a worry with this floor! Install with ease using its click-lock technology, and reduce installation costs with its pre-attached, acoustic underlayment. features: Power Boil on Tri- and Dual-Ring Elements - this cooktop has a 3,000W tri-ring element and a 2,400W dual-ring element that allow for different pan sizes to be used for rapid boiling,Precision Temperature Control - set your burner to an exact degree, not just high, medium or low, using a smart pan, the cooktop maintains a specific temperature – from 100 to 500 degrees; perfect for sauces, candies and frying,Guided Cooking - connect a smart pan to your cooktop and your burners will adjust time and temperature based on a video-guided recipe in the app; choose from thousands of recipes and get perfectly cooked food (Pan sold separately),Glide Touch Controls - choose from 11 different heat settings with one easy swipe for total heat control,Easy Clean Surface - a smooth glass surface and glide touch controls makes cleaning up messes simpler than ever on this easy clean electric cooktop,Smart Cookware Rebate - smart pans and a wireless sous vide probe easily pair with this smart cooktop to ensure you get the perfect cooking results; earn a rebate for a free 11-in Hestan Cue Smart Pan,Built-in WiFi - this smart cooktop features Built-In WiFi so you can monitor your burners and view power levels, precision temperature, or on/off,Synchronized Elements - connect and control two cooktop burners as one to create a bigger cooking surface for pans such as griddles,Synchronized Fan and Lights - synchronize your cooktop and GE Profile over-the-range microwave or hood so that your fan or hood and lights automatically come on when a burner is activated with Chef Connect

descriptionHtml: This Over-the-Range Microwave with Sensor Cooking conveniently provides optimal cooking results, while precise glass touch controls let you easily select cooking functions. Bespoke kitchen appliances are now available in complementary colors to the Bespoke 4-Door Flex Refrigerator. Create your kitchen space in your style in White Glass, Navy Steel, or Tuscan Steel
features: Large Oven Capacity: A large 2.1 cu ft oven capacity accommodates a variety of dishes so you can prep large meals quickly,Sensor Cook: Automatically adjusts cooking time for optimal results,Glass Touch Controls: A modern, glass touchpad provides precise control with a seamless, integrated design,4-Speed 400 CFM Hood Ventilation System: The bottom of this Over-the-Range Microwave features a powerful ventilation system that quickly and quietly eliminates steam and odors from the kitchen,Eco Mode: Our Eco Mode button conserves power by turning off the display when not in use and is more convenient than unplugging the microwave when not in use,Ceramic Enamel Interior and Fingerprint Resistant Finish: A beautiful and durable scratch-resistant ceramic blue interior is easy to keep clean while the Stainless Fingerprint Resistant finish(1) on the outside maintains an everyday, beautiful shine,LED Display: A large LED display makes settings and timing clearly visible for greater cooking convenience, and the blue color of the digital display provides a stylish accent to your kitchen interior(2),(1)Bespoke White Glass finish is not fingerprint resistant,(2)Bespoke White Glass finish LED display is white
name: Samsung 2.1-cu ft 1000-Watt Over-the-Range Microwave with Sensor Cooking (White Glass)

description: The Frigidaire Gallery 1.9 cu. ft. Over-The-Range Microwave with Sensor Cook, delivers delicious meals by automatically determining and setting appropriate power levels and cook time. Plus, changing your filter has never been more convenient with our Push-to-Open PureAir®  Filter Door and filter indicator light. Also includes a Frigidaire PureAir®  Filter, and features our fingerprint resistant, Smudge-Proof®  Stainless Steel finish.
descriptionHtml: The Frigidaire Gallery 1.9 cu. ft. Over-The-Range Microwave with Sensor Cook, delivers delicious meals by automatically determining and setting appropriate power levels and cook time. Plus, changing your filter has never been more convenient with our Push-to-Open PureAir® Filter Door and filter indicator light. Also includes a Frigidaire PureAir® Filter, and features our fingerprint resistant, Smudge-Proof® Stainless Steel finish.
features: Ensures great tasting results every time with Sensor Cook,Capture odors and circulate fresher air with PureAir Filter,Filter change made easy with Push-to-Open PureAir Filter Door,Microwave doubles as a ventilation hood to circulate fresher air,Easily wipe away spills with Effortless Clean™ Interior,Clear, bright exterior and interior view with LED lighting,Start cooking meals faster with 6 Quick Start options,Resists fingerprints and cleans easily,Reheat to perfection every time with Sensor Reheat
name: Frigidaire Gallery 1.9-cu ft 1000-Watt Over-the-Range Microwave with Sensor Cooking (Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel)

description: A perfect space saving solution for small living spaces, RVs, Boats, or anyplace you need big cleaning in a compact size. This powerful, easy to use, portable dishwasher holds up to 6 place settings and offers 7 powerful wash programs. It's easy to install, has simple one-touch digital controls, and easily sits right on your countertops or a sturdy tabletop
descriptionHtml: A perfect space saving solution for small living spaces, RVs, Boats, or anyplace you need big cleaning in a compact size. This powerful, easy to use, portable dishwasher holds up to 6 place settings and offers 7 powerful wash programs. It's easy to install, has simple one-touch digital controls, and easily sits right on your countertops or a sturdy tabletop
features: COMPACT DESIGN: This convenient dishwasher has a 6-place setting capacity, making it ideal for small-sized houses, apartments, dorms, boats and campers/RVs,SIX-PLACE SETTING: The six-place setting capacity allows you to wash a variety of dishes (up to 10-inches in diameter) and includes folding down rack shelves and a cutlery basket,QUICK INSTALLATION: Features a quick connect assembly with accessories and adapters included to easily connect directly to your faucet,SEVEN WASHING PROGRAMS: You'll get full size dishwasher cleaning in a countertop sized compact unit that offers seven wash programs - Heavy, Normal, Baby Care, Light, Glass, Speed 45 Min, Self Clean,EXTRA-DRYING FUNCTION: This feature adds extra heat to the final rinse to enhance drying results, but can only be used with the following programs - Heavy, Normal, Light, Glass, Baby Care,SPEED WASH and SELF-CLEANING: If you need dishes cleaned quickly, the Speed cycle lets you get items clean in only 45 minutes. The Self Cleaning program provides an effective cleaning of the dishwasher itself,CHILD LOCK: Option allows you to lock the buttons on the control panel so children cannot accidentally start the dishwasher,EASY-TO-USE CONTROLS: The LED digital controls give you a clear picture-view of wash controls and the Rinse Aid/Water Supply Failure indicators light up when dishwasher is low on rinse and that no water is reaching the dishwasher,DURABLE AND POWERFUL: With an enduring stainless steel heavy-duty interior tub you can be assured that this machine is ready to stand up to your everyday cleaning
name: Farberware 19.7-in Portable Countertop Dishwasher (Black)

description: Perfect for apartments, office kitchens or any small-sized kitchens; offers full-size power in a compact design. With a height of only 17.24 inches, this unit will fit between most countertop and cabinetry. Spacious cavity loads up to six standard place settings. description: The FourSide jar’s square shape blends much better than traditional round jars. No tamper/plunger needed. Professional-grade jar is compatible with all Blendtec blender models (not compatible with Blendtec mix n' Blend models). The jar also generates more friction, heating soups and hot drinks quickly and easily. It’s also especially good for grinding grains and making smaller quantities.

description: Let this little machine do all the magic for you! It's small, space-saving, and powerful enough to handle your daily dishwashing needs. Just connect the dishwasher to a water tank or faucet yourself. The mini dishwasher has upgraded inside space, holding up to 10.5-inch plates. It also has two enhanced functions: Auto-Open function provides effective drying performance; UV Hygiene Program ensures no food particles are left behind.
descriptionHtml: Let this little machine do all the magic for you! It's small, space-saving, and powerful enough to handle your daily dishwashing needs. Just connect the dishwasher to a water tank or faucet yourself. The mini dishwasher has upgraded inside space, holding up to 10.5-inch plates. It also has two enhanced functions: Auto-Open function provides effective drying performance; UV Hygiene Program ensures no food particles are left behind.
features: The ultra compact design allows the dishwasher to wash 30 plus items which is ideal for small houses, apartments, dorms and boats.,NORMAL, RAPID, STEAM, FRUIT, GLASS washing programs, and AIR REFRESH extra drying mode meet all your daily needs.,Hygiene wash cycle boosts water temperature to 162°F - 192°F tackling heavily soiled dishes and suitable for cleaning baby bottles.,No installation needed - add water manually in the 5 Liter built-in water tank.,Circulation of FRESH AIR removes moisture and odor, keeping your plates and machine cavity dry and fresh for a long time.,2 enhanced functions: AUTO-OPEN provides effective drying and UV Hygiene Program ensures there will be no particles left behind.,The dishwasher cleans with less effort only consumes 6L of water per wash cycle and Saves 60% of the amount used when handwashing.,LED Digital Display, See-Through Viewing Window, Child Lock, and Leak Protection allow for an easy and safe operation.,1-Year Warranty:  1-Year limited manufacturer warranty
name: Comfee 16.5-in Portable Countertop Dishwasher (Black), 62-dBA

description: A perfect space saving solution for small living spaces, RVs, Boats, or anyplace you need big cleaning in a compact size.  This powerful, easy to use, portable dishwasher holds up to 6 place settings and offers 6 powerful wash programs. It's easy to install, has simple one-touch digital controls, and easily sits right on your countertops or a sturdy tabletop.
descriptionHtml: A perfect space saving solution for small living spaces, RVs, Boats, or anyplace you need big cleaning in a compact size. This powerful, easy to use, portable dishwasher holds up to 6 place settings and offers 6 powerful wash programs. It's easy to install, has simple one-touch digital controls, and easily sits right on your countertops or a sturdy tabletop.
features: COMPACT DESIGN: This convenient dishwasher has a 6-place setting capacity, making it ideal for small-sized houses, apartments, dorms, boats and campers/RVs,SIX-PLACE SETTING: The six-place setting capacity allows you to wash a variety of dishes (up to 10-inches in diameter) and includes folding down rack shelves and a cutlery basket,QUICK INSTALLATION: Features a quick connect assembly with accessories and adapters included to easily connect directly to your faucet,SIX WASHING PROGRAMS: You'll get full size dishwasher cleaning in a countertop sized compact unit that offers six wash programs - Heavy, Normal, Baby Care, Light, Speed 45 Min, Self Clean,EXTRA-DRYING FUNCTION: This feature adds extra heat to the final rinse to enhance drying results, but can only be used with the following programs - Heavy, Normal, Light, Glass, Baby Care,SPEED WASH AND SELF-CLEANING: If you need dishes cleaned quickly, the Speed cycle lets you get items clean in only 45 minutes. The Self Cleaning program provides an effective cleaning of the dishwasher itself,CHILD LOCK: Option allows you to lock the buttons on the control panel so children cannot accidentally start the dishwasher,EASY-TO-USE CONTROLS: The LED digital controls give you a clear picture-view of wash controls and the Rinse Aid/Water Supply Failure indicators light up when dishwasher is low on rinse and that no water is reaching the dishwasher,DURABLE AND POWERFUL: With an enduring stainless steel heavy-duty interior tub you can be assured that this machine is ready to stand up to your everyday cleaning
name: Farberware Professional 21.8-in Portable Countertop Dishwasher (White) ENERGY STAR

description: Let this little machine do all the magic for you! It's small, space-saving, and powerful enough to handle your daily dishwashing needs. Just connect the dishwasher to a water tank or faucet yourself. The mini dishwasher has upgraded inside space, holding up to 10.5-inch plates. It also has two enhanced functions: Auto-Open function provides effective drying performance; UV Hygiene Program ensures no food particles are left behind.
descriptionHtml: Let this little machine do all the magic for you! It's small, space-saving, and powerful enough to handle your daily dishwashing needs. Just connect the dishwasher to a water tank or faucet yourself. The mini dishwasher has upgraded inside space, holding up to 10.5-inch plates. It also has two enhanced functions: Auto-Open function provides effective drying performance; UV Hygiene Program ensures no food particles are left behind.
features: The ultra compact design allows the dishwasher to wash 30 plus items which is ideal for small houses, apartments, dorms and boats.,NORMAL, RAPID, STEAM, FRUIT, GLASS washing programs, and AIR REFRESH extra drying mode meet all your daily needs.,Hygiene wash cycle boosts water temperature to 162°F - 192°F tackling heavily soiled dishes and suitable for cleaning baby bottles.,No installation needed - add water manually in the upgraded 6 Liter built-in water tank.,Larger capacity inside than a normal mini dishwasher, which allows you to load more with less space,2 enhanced functions: AUTO-OPEN provides effective drying and UV Hygiene Program ensures there will be no particles left behind.,LED Digital Display, See-Through Viewing Window, Child Lock, and Leak Protection allow for an easy and safe operation.,The dishwasher cleans with less effort only consumes 6L of water per wash cycle and Saves 60% of the amount used when handwashing.,1-Year Warranty:  1-Year limited manufacturer warranty
name: Comfee 16.5-in Portable Countertop Dishwasher (White), 62-dBA

When you want flooring designed for you and the demands of your life, there's a SMARTCORE for that.

description: Do you want to give your room a brand new, modern look and at a low cost? Look no further than our assortment of majestic tiles! The dramatic 18-in x 18-in self-stick vinyl tile, featuring classic marbles and stones designs, delivers the appealing look of real stone in a premium performing light commercial grade vinyl tile. Our tiles can be used in any room in your home including the kitchen, dining room, bedrooms, bathrooms, foyers and basements. No messy glue or adhesives needed. Just peel and stick the majestic tiles to a flat and dry surface and show off your beautiful new room to all your friends and neighbors. 22.5 Square feet per box (10 tiles per box).

description: Get the right clean for your dishes with this heavy-duty dishwasher. Finish the job in half the time with the 1-hour wash cycle and rely on the soil sensor to adjust to the soil levels of your dishes for the most thorough clean.
descriptionHtml: Get the right clean for your dishes with this heavy-duty dishwasher. Finish the job in half the time with the 1-hour wash cycle and rely on the soil sensor to adjust to the soil levels of your dishes for the most thorough clean.
features: Clean dishes quicker with the 1-Hour Wash cycle,Get a cycle that matches your soil level with the soil sensor,Normal cycle - use for normal amounts of food soil to clean up leftover messes from your day-to-day meals,Heavy cycle - take care of baked-on messes and other heavily soiled items without the extra elbow grease by adding extra time to the cycle,High Temperature wash option - choose this option when additional cleaning of items like baby bottles, glassware or dishes is required,Heated dry option - use a clean, dry dish straight from the dishwasher thanks to added heat for drying - for optimal drying results, use this option with rinse aid,Designed, engineered and assembled in the USA with American Pride

description: STAINMASTER 100% waterproof Alexandria Stone luxury vinyl tile is a classic stone look featuring subtle terracotta and grey tones and a soft stone embossed texture, creating an inviting look for a variety of living spaces. Our vinyl tile offers long lasting, rigid core flooring ready for your active household. Our ACTIVELIFE SHIELD™ provides the dent, abrasion, and scratch resistance that busy homes demand. It’s waterproof, stain-resistant, and easy to clean so everyday accidents are not a worry with this floor! Install with ease using its click-lock system technology, and reduce installation costs with its pre-attached, acoustic underlayment. And, finally, have peace of mind knowing STAINMASTER vinyl tile floors are backed by a lifetime residential limited warranty and 15-Year light commercial limited warranty. Long-lasting, stylish, and durable, STAINMASTER Luxury Vinyl Tile Flooring is perfect for your home. Exclusively at Lowe’s.

description: Redesign any space in the home or office with the Palazzo 12-inch x 24-inch Self Adhesive Vinyl Floor Tiles. These farmhouse inspired rectangular vinyl tiles are available in various styles that have the look and feel of natural stone, poured cement or honed wood.    Vinyl self-adhesive tiles can be used in any room in your home including the kitchen, dining room, bedrooms, bathrooms, foyers, basements and more. No messy glue or adhesives needed. Just peel and stick the Palazzo tiles to a flat & dry surface.  DIY instructions included, no professional installation tools are required.  40 Square Feet per Box (20 Tiles per Box).

description: The Loseta Collection innovatively combines texture, color, and pattern to create a product that allows you to express any vision. The combination of Loseta’s ProTx UV-cured topcoat finish, which provides an illustrious 28mil wear layer, and fiberglass layer results in an unmatched dimensional stability, redefining commercial and residential standards for LVT. description: Perfect for apartments, office kitchens or any small-sized kitchens; offers full-size power in a compact design. description: "Get help all around your kitchen with the BLACK+DECKER kitchen wand™, a cordless 6in1 kitchen multitool. It is the perfect appliance to help you create all sorts of dishes. Built-In rechargeable battery gives you up to 30 minutes of continuous runtime†. The wand base contains clear battery state-of-charge indicator lights and an adjustable speed dial for control over the power chosen. The 6in1 kit includes food-prep-focused attachments including an immersion blender, whisk, and milk frother, as well as innovative attachments like a can opener, wine opener, and 2in1 salt and pepper grinder. The kit also includes a measuring cup and lid, 2 storage cases with insert trays, and a charging dock and cord to minimize the amount of space kitchen wand takes in your kitchen. The ultimate kitchen sidekick™. Based on a fully charged wand base with immersion blender attachment, running with no load."
descriptionHtml: "Get help all around your kitchen with the BLACK+DECKER kitchen wand™, a cordless 6in1 kitchen multitool. It is the perfect appliance to help you create all sorts of dishes. description: Built on the belief that modern life needs modern solutions, GE Profile Appliances are designed to make daily life simpler by incorporating Smart Home technology and cutting-edge features in every appliance. GE Profile’s sleek design and quality engineering will give your kitchen the most up-to-date look and the best innovative performance you’ve been looking for.
descriptionHtml: Built on the belief that modern life needs modern solutions, GE Profile Appliances are designed to make daily life simpler by incorporating Smart Home technology and cutting-edge features in every appliance. GE Profile’s sleek design and quality engineering will give your kitchen the most up-to-date look and the best innovative performance you’ve been looking for.
features: Power Boil on Two Tri-Ring Elements - this cooktop has 3,600 and 3,000 tri-ring elements that allow for different pan sizes to be used for rapid boiling,Precision Temperature Control - set your burner to an exact degree, not just high, medium or low, using a smart pan, the cooktop maintains a specific temperature – from 100 to 500 degrees; perfect for sauces, candies and frying,Guided Cooking - connect a smart pan to your cooktop and your burners will adjust time and temperature based on a video-guided recipe in the app; choose from thousands of recipes and get perfectly cooked food (Pan sold separately),Glide Touch Controls - choose from 11 different heat settings with one easy swipe for total heat control,Easy Clean Surface - a smooth glass surface and glide touch controls makes cleaning up messes simpler than ever on this easy clean electric cooktop,Smart Cookware Rebate - smart pans and a wireless sous vide probe easily pair with this smart cooktop to ensure you get the perfect cooking results; earn a rebate for a free 11-in Hestan Cue Smart Pan,Built-in WiFi - this smart cooktop features Built-In WiFi so you can monitor your burners and view power levels, precision temperature, or on/off,Synchronized Elements - connect and control two cooktop burners as one to create a bigger cooking surface for pans such as griddles,Synchronized Fan and Lights - synchronize your cooktop and GE Profile over-the-range microwave or hood so that your fan or hood and lights automatically come on when a burner is activated with Chef Connect
name: GE Profile 36-in 5 Burners Smooth Surface (Radiant) Stainless Steel Smart Electric Cooktop

Or fire up the 10/6-inch Dual-Choice™ element of the glass cooktop with the pan you want and the power you need. Plus, we stand behind it witha 10-year limited parts warranty.
features: Maytag® exclusive electric cooktop with reversible grill and griddle - boil, pan fry, grill, sear and griddle all on one cooktop,10/6-inch Dual-Choice™ element gives you the ability to cook with the pan you want and the power you need,10-Year limited parts warranty on the glass cooktop and element,Built with heavy-duty, die-cast metal knobs to give you dependable and responsive power control,The hot surface indicator light illuminates when your electric cooktop surface is hot to the touch, even after the heating element has been turned off,Quick grill and griddle preheat gets meals to the table fast,Flip and grip built in handles make flipping between grill and griddle easy,As a long-standing American company, we pack over a century of knowledge, experience and dependability into every product
name: Maytag 30-in 4 Burners Smooth Surface (Radiant) Stainless Steel Electric Cooktop

description: Are you a fan of a good old-fashioned soda shop… miss the days of dance contests, music on the beach and car hops. Then grab your sweetheart and take a trip back in time with our soda pop shoppe Collection. Tiles are inspired by the classic look and style of the soda shops we all grew to love from a time when things were simple and classy. These retro inspired tiles are available in several popular checkered color options that are sure to look great in any room of the home. So grab a milkshake or enjoy an ice-cold pop and bring the vintage vibes into your home with these retro inspired floor tiles.

descriptionHtml: The Ninja® Professional Blender 1000 features a sleek design and outstanding performance with 1000 watts of professional power. description: Free up space above your cooktop with the new, beautifully designed Smart SLIM Microwave. This combination microwave with hood packs in powerful performance and technology you love in a slim, space efficient size
descriptionHtml: Free up space above your cooktop with the new, beautifully designed Smart SLIM Microwave. This combination microwave with hood packs in powerful performance and technology you love in a slim, space efficient size
features: 400 CFM Hood Ventilation : Even in its slim size, this hood has a powerful 400 CFM ventilation system that quickly removes steam and odors that result from cooking,Wi-Fi and Voice Control : Adjust settings with your voice or with your smartphone by using the SmartThings App; Using a voice assistant, like Samsung Bixby, Amazon Alexa, or Google Assistant, you can tell your microwave what you want it to do(1),Ceramic Enamel Interior : A beautiful ceramic blue interior is easy to keep clean,Fingerprint Resistant Finish : Fingerprint resistant for an everyday beautiful finish,1100 Watt Output Power : Save time with impressive 1100W output power that enables you to cook quickly and evenly; Larger dishes are also cooked more thoroughly when the microwave has greater power performance,Dual Wide Grease Filter : Trap more airborne particles, such as oil and grease, improving hood performance with this large dual wide grease filter built into the hood,Halogen Cooktop Light : Halogen lighting illuminates evenly over your entire cooktop,(1)Available on Android and iOS devices - A Wi-Fi connection and a Samsung account are required; Bixby is Samsung’s brand of Artificial intelligence (AI),(1)Google is a trademark of Google LLC
name: Samsung Smart SLIM 1.1-cu ft 1100-Watt Smart Over-the-Range Microwave (Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel)

description: A stylish design for a seamless and modern look, this over-the-range microwave features large 1.7 cu. ft. capacity and a fingerprint resistant finish.
descriptionHtml: A stylish design for a seamless and modern look, this over-the-range microwave features large 1.7 cu. ft. capacity and a fingerprint resistant finish.
features: Large Capacity:  Accommodates a variety of snacks and meal items to prepare foods quickly and easily,Fingerprint Resistant: Helps reduce smudges for an everyday great appearance,Premium Design: A stylish appliance with a big window design for easy viewing, clean lines, and color options to enhance the look and feel of your kitchen,300 CFM Ventilation System: A powerful ventilation system quickly and quietly eliminates steam, fumes, and odors form the kitchen; the nearly silent system clears the air with 300 cubic feet per minute of turbo ventilation,LED Display: Striking blue LED Display adds clarity and style to your kitchen,Eco Mode (Reduces Standby Power): Saves energy and reduces the carbon footprint by turning off the display when not in use,10 Power Levels : Different power levels to cook a variety of foods,1000 Watts of Cooking Power: Powerful cooking for boiling, reheating, and defrosting,Charcoal/Grease Vent Filter: Replaceable filter takes grease and other impurities out of the air

description: Design Inspiration - Incorporating chevron shapes and symmetry Perfection Floor Tile sought to create dynamic designs that evoke balance and harmony. Chevrons, angles, and geometric outlines define the Geo Collection refined yet bold aesthetic. Great for entrance ways, mud rooms and to add a dramatic look to your kitchen. Every Perfection Floor Tile floor is created with superior craftsmanship, ingenuity, and sustainable practices. Perfection Floor Tile's are easy to install, hidden interlocking, floating floor system. Simply: clean, measure, place, trim and enjoy! No glue or adhesives necessary. Our tiles are made with 100% pure vinyl floor: No carcinogens, toxins, or harsh chemicals. Great for family rooms, bathrooms, kitchens, basements, attic, and playrooms. Ideal for offices, warehouses, schools, and government offices.

description: Mohawk Elite waterproof vinyl tile flooring offers beautiful designer wood and stone looks with worry-free performance. Ice Cap Marble evokes soft white travertine with shades of gray for a classic feel. The premium LVT is designed to repel household spills and pet accidents, making it remarkably easy to clean. Ideal for any level and any room in your home, Elite can be installed even in high-traffic areas or damp spaces such as basements and bathrooms. Mohawk interlocking tiles make installation a snap, and DIY-friendly built-in underlayment saves time on installation. Elite LVT includes a limited lifetime residential warranty and a 10-year limited light commercial warranty. Mohawk is a worldwide leader in flooring solutions. Committed to innovation, performance, and sustainability, many of Mohawk collections have changed the face of flooring. The brand is renowned for creating unique products that add style and value to any space.

features: Powerful Immersion Blender - blend up smoothies, shakes, sauces and purees with ease thanks to a high performance immersion blender with 500w of power in a multi-purpose hand blender,2- Speed Hand Blender - simple to clean and use, this versatile dual-speed hand blender switches smoothly from low to high speed, so you can blend all your food and drink recipes with ease,One-Handed Operation - easily add ingredients while you blend thanks to a hand-held blender that ergonomically fits for single-hand operation,Blending and Chopping Attachments - blend smoothies or chop vegetables with ease with the stainless-steel blender accessories and catch even the smallest portions of herbs, nuts and spices with a chopping jar that attaches right to your hand-held blender,Whisk Attachment - beat eggs, whip up batters and more thanks to an immersion blender with a whisk attachment that is easily removed for quick cleanup,Chopping Jar and Additional Attachments - achieve perfect smoothie consistency or chop vegetables with stainless-steel accessories and catch the smallest portions of chopped herbs, nuts and spices in a jar that attaches right to your hand-held blender,Easy-to-Use Attachments - this well-designed immersion blender with detachable attachments make it easy to change them out for different uses and to clean them
name: GE 2-Speed Stainless Steel 500-Watt Immersion Blender with Accessory Jar

description: STAINMASTER 100% waterproof Tuscana Marble luxury vinyl tile features a Carrera marble look with elegant grey veining for a luxurious look in any living space. Our vinyl tile offers long lasting, rigid core flooring ready for your active household. Our ACTIVELIFE SHIELD™ provides the dent, abrasion, and scratch resistance that busy homes demand. It’s waterproof, stain-resistant, and easy to clean so everyday accidents are not a worry with this floor! Install with ease using its click-lock system technology, and reduce installation costs with its pre-attached, acoustic underlayment. And, finally, have peace of mind knowing STAINMASTER vinyl tile floors are backed by a lifetime residential limited warranty and 15-Year light commercial limited warranty. Long-lasting, stylish, and durable, STAINMASTER Luxury Vinyl Tile Flooring is perfect for your home. Exclusively at Lowe’s.

description: Nouveax HDPC Rigid Core Vinyl Tile Flooring couples the look of real tile with the exceptional performance only a rigid plastic composite core can deliver. These tiles are embossed to feel like real tile and offer a contemporary, bold, and beautiful style to your home or office. Perfect for high traffic areas, including kitchens, bathrooms and basements. The tiles are 100% waterproof and require no acclimation prior to installation. HDPC Rigid Core increased strength and density hides sub-floor imperfections, floats over most existing hard surface floors, and is perfect for the DIY homeowner. HDPC Rigid Core Vinyl Tile Flooring is combined with an attached foam pad that reduces sound transmission and increases comfort when walking. Nouveax HDPC Rigid Core Vinyl Tile Flooring is EPA (TSCA title VI) compliant and also has the coveted GreenGuard Gold certification, which provides safer and healthier indoor home and work environments. Waterproof peace of mind, the added benefit of a safer product, and Nouveax’s tough Urethane Ceramic finish provides the right flooring solution for active families or office spaces.

description: Perfection Floor Tile’s seaport look transcends through time. The Mystic Plank Collection will bring the look of salt-worn plank that will blend harmoniously with any room. Perfection Floor Tile interlocking vinyl floor tile can be installed almost anywhere in your home, meaning you can have a wood look in areas where wood is not recommended, such as the bathroom or laundry room. This flooring is also easy to clean and for the DIY person, it is easy to install. All this, plus comfort under foot. Every Perfection Floor Tile floor is created with superior craftsmanship, ingenuity, and sustainable practices. Perfection Floor Tile are easy to install, hidden interlocking, floating floor system. Simply: clean, measure, place, trim and enjoy! No glue or adhesives necessary. Our tiles are made with 100% pure vinyl floor: No carcinogens, toxins, or harsh chemicals. Great for family rooms, bathrooms, kitchens, basements, attic, and playrooms. Ideal for offices, warehouses, schools, and government offices.perfection. Striking tonal patterns and contrasting visuals. These beautiful tiles are warmer to the touch, kinder to the feet, and easy to care for in any room of your home.

Every Perfection Floor Tile floor is created with superior craftsmanship, ingenuity, and sustainable practices. Perfection Floor Tile are easy to install, hidden interlocking, floating floor system. Simply: clean, measure, place, trim and enjoy! No glue or adhesives necessary. Our tiles are made with 100% pure vinyl floor: No carcinogens, toxins, or harsh chemicals. Great for family rooms, bathrooms, kitchens, basements, attic, and playrooms. Ideal for offices, warehouses, schools, and government offices.perfection. Striking tonal patterns and contrasting visuals. These beautiful tiles are warmer to the touch, kinder to the feet, and easy to care for in any room of your home.

description:
The InSinkErator Power 15SS 3/4 HP Garbage Disposal offers a hygienic, convenient and environmentally responsible way to rid your kitchen of food scraps. Septic-safe for properly maintained septic systems, this compact garbage disposal quickly grinds food waste into tiny particles that easily flush down the kitchen drain. Part of the InSinkErator Power Series, InSinkErator garbage disposals designed to prevent clogs by grinding food scraps finer*, the Power 15SS has a 3/4 HP, heavy-duty Dura-Drive induction motor with more jam-busting torque to power through tough food scraps like peach pits. In addition to reduced sound and rust-resistant, stainless steel grind components for durability, the compact design fits easily under the kitchen sink. This EZ Connect InSinkErator garbage disposal has Lift and Latch technology for easy installation. The perfect complement to every kitchen since 1938, InSinkErator helps you Kitchen Better.
*Compared to Standard Series.

description: The KRAUS WasteGuard Garbage Disposal is perfect for homeowners who use their kitchen regularly and want to keep cleanup simple. The high-speed 3800 RPM 1/2 Horsepower motor provides instant power for fast and reliable grinding of food waste. The continuous-feed disposal grinds waste into small particles, helping reduce food waste and garbage bags going to landfills. Built with durable stainless steel components and ABS housing for lasting quality. EZLock mounting assembly locks into place with a turn of the hand for easy DIY installation. Motor-saving shut-off technology helps prevent damage in case of blockage. Anti-vibration mounting system and motor with low decibel output help ensure quiet operation. Fits standard 3-1/2-in. drain openings. Comes with power cord, flange, and stopper.
descriptionHtml: The KRAUS WasteGuard Garbage Disposal is perfect for homeowners who use their kitchen regularly and want to keep cleanup simple. The high-speed 3800 RPM 1/2 Horsepower motor provides instant power for fast and reliable grinding of food waste. The continuous-feed disposal grinds waste into small particles, helping reduce food waste and garbage bags going to landfills. Built with durable stainless steel components and ABS housing for lasting quality. EZLock mounting assembly locks into place with a turn of the hand for easy DIY installation. Motor-saving shut-off technology helps prevent damage in case of blockage. Anti-vibration mounting system and motor with low decibel output help ensure quiet operation. Fits standard 3-1/2-in. drain openings. Comes with power cord, flange, and stopper.
features: Powerful grinding of everyday food scraps with superior 3800 RPM TO 1/3 HP ratio that eliminates waste in seconds,Quick-connect EZLock mounting assembly with mounting flange locks into place with no plumber’s putty needed,Dimensions 5-1/4 in L x 8-3/4 in W x 13-7/8 in H; grinding chamber 27 oz; works with 3-1/2 in drain and 1-1/2 in plumbing,Installation-ready kit: 1/2 HP garbage disposal, drain and dishwasher connector, quick-connect mounting assembly with stainless steel rim, drain stopper/waste plunger for stubborn food scraps, pre-installed power cord, rubber gaskets for a perfect seal,High-speed MagnaGrind permanent-magnet motor provides instant power to the grinder for faster operation than induction motors which take time to reach optimal speed; motor-saving shut off stops power in the event of a blockage to help prevent damage,Quiet operation with anti-vibration mounting system and low decibel output motor for quieter grinding; solid stainless steel grinding components encased in durable ABS thermoplastic housing offer greater resistance to damage and corrosion,Continuous feed disposal is activated via wall switch or air switch, allowing you to shred large quantities of waste continuously for faster and easier operation than batch-feed disposals; slide food scraps into the drain and watch them disappear,Eco-friendly product cuts down on plastic garbage bag use, grinds up and condenses food scraps for quicker breakdown; septic safe with most septic systems in accordance with manufacturer guidelines (note: some foods are not compatible with septic),Universal design works with kitchen sinks with standard round 3-1/2 in drain opening and 1-1/2 in standard kitchen plumbing connections; 5-year limited warranty; certifications cUPC, ETL, and ISTA
name: Kraus WasteGuard Corded 1/2-HP Continuous Feed Noise Insulation Garbage Disposal

description: Every DIYer or professional tradesperson needs a socket wrench set to complete a wide variety of jobs. The CRAFTSMAN 11-piece Metric 3/8-in drive 6-point shallow socket set includes a continuous range of sockets from 10mm to 21mm. These sockets are made with high-strength chromium vanadium steel, promising a longer usable life. Each socket features a shallow design that can access the most stubborn fasteners in the tightest spots. It also comes with large, highly visible markings for quick size identification. Each socket delivers more torque, which means you can loosen nuts and bolts without breaking a sweat. It can be used with any 3/8-in ratchet, torque wrench, extension, or breaker bar. It can also be attached to a wobble attachment or join so you can release fasteners a few degrees off straight. Get this set of high-torque 3/8-in drive 6-point shallow sockets at Lowes.com today.

description: The InSinkErator Evolution 35SS 5/8 HP Garbage Disposal offers a hygienic, convenient and environmentally responsible way to rid your kitchen of food scraps. Septic-safe for properly maintained septic systems, this compact garbage disposal quickly grinds food waste into tiny particles that easily flush down the kitchen drain. Part of the InSinkErator Advanced Series, premium InSinkErator garbage disposals with patented SoundSeal technology for quieter operation than standard disposals, plus superior grind performance for tough and fibrous food scraps, the Evolution 35SS has a 5/8 HP, heavy-duty Dura-Drive induction motor. It provides jam-busting torque with stainless steel grind components in a compact design that fits under the kitchen sink. This EZ Connect InSinkErator garbage disposal also has an EZ Connect Hardwire Adapter, EZ Grip Handles, EZ Removable Dishwasher Inlet Plug, and Lift and Latch technology for easy installation. Since 1938, InSinkErator helps you Kitchen Better.

description: Offering advanced features and practical convenience, the Project Source PSD-90-SL compact slim line 3/4 HP garbage disposal makes food disposal safer, faster, and easier than conventional garbage disposers. Featuring a compact, slim line design, this kitchen garbage disposal unit with standard 3-bolt mounting system allows for convenient installation in tight under sink spaces, saving you valuable storage space for your cleaning supplies. Operating on 110V 60Hz power, the powerful 3/4 HP 2700 RPM high-speed permanent magnet motor boasts anti-jam stainless steel impellers to cut through tough food waste without jamming, offering fast continuous feed operation. The torque master grinding system uses computer designed balanced components to provide superior torque grind speed and long system life, ensuring less vibration and quieter operation. To protect against odors, this 3/4 HP garbage disposal is treated with a unique agent unlike any other garbage disposer to eliminate foul smells from stinking up your kitchen. A removable splash guard is ideal for easy cleaning and replacement.

description: Cut a huge variety of materials while saving money with this variety pack of Cricut® machine mats which cover everything from delicate paper to heavy cardstock. Each reusable mat keeps your material secure for a clean cut and easy removals once the cut is done. Each mat is made for the longest possible life and the best adhesion. With two mats included, you can load one in your Cricut machine for cutting as you prep the next. For use with Cricut Maker® and Cricut Explore® cutting machines. Use the LightGrip Mat for standard paper, light cardstock, and vellum; StandardGrip for heavy cardstock, iron-on, and vinyl; StrongGrip for specialty cardstock, matboard, backed fabric, and more. Tips: Keep the clear film cover on the mat when storing to keep mat free from paper scraps and dust. Use the scraper to scrape away excess pieces and the spatula to carefully remove cut images. To ensure best performance, use the recommended material types on the mats.

description: Offering reliability and durability at an affordable price, the InSinkErator Badger® 5 - 1/2 HP Continuous Feed garbage disposal without cord is a dependable and economical choice. The garbage disposer features a heavy-duty 1/2 HP Dura-Drive® Induction Motor that quietly delivers consistent performance year after year. Its 26 Oz.. capacity grind chamber allows you to dispose of food waste right into the sink, keeping your food preparation area clean and reducing the amount of bagged garbage in your kitchen. With a 1725 RPM motor and Continuous Feed, the badger 5 garbage disposal effectively grinds large amounts of difficult food waste. Built to withstand long-term wear, it features rugged, Galvanized Steel construction that delivers superior durability. Functional as well as durable, the kitchen garbage disposer has a compact, space-saving design that provides more storage space under the sink. This InSinkErator garbage disposal has a patented Quick Lock® mounting system for easy installation and replacement of garbage disposers. The Quick Lock mount is completely compatible with all InSinkErator models. When it's time to upgrade or replace, simply twist off the old mount and twist on the new one. Includes garbage disposer, flange, stopper, assembly components, Quick Lock components and user's manual. Power cord not included (sold separately for installations where a power outlet is present). InSinkErator power cord accessory CRD-00 recommended. The InSinkErator Badger 5 garbage disposal is assembled in the USA and carries a We Come To You® 3-year in-home limited warranty.

description: The TEKTON 1/4 Inch Drive 6-Point Socket and Ratchet Set includes every socket from 5/32 to 9/16 inch and 4 to 14 mm with no skipped sizes. The set comes equipped with a 90-Tooth quick-release ratchet as well as a universal joint, power socket adapter, and extension—which are not often found in most sets. All of the tools come stored in a sturdy carrying case. The 6-point socket openings are ideal for working with hex-shaped fasteners and designed to grip the sides and not the corners of the fastener heads, preventing round-off. An extended length allows the deep socket to fit over long fasteners and reach into recessed areas. The large, die-stamped markings are permanently impressed into the material and optimized for readability. A mirror chrome-plated finish protects against corrosion and easily wipes clean.

description: The Capri Tools ADVANCED SERIES sockets and bit sockets are made for the most demanding professionals. Crafted from custom forged premium steel, they undergo proprietary heat treatment and are precisely machined to perform in the toughest situations. The bits are forged with premium S2 steel. These S2 steel bits are exceptionally strong and durable; they withstand high torque and do not twist, protecting both the bit and the fastener. Our proprietary advanced heat treatment process further enhances the properties of the S2 and Chrome Vanadium steel alloy to achieve the optimal balance of strength and performance. All bits have chamfered end to ensure a smooth fit onto fasteners. The sockets are made from premium Chrome Vanadium steel, plated with our SmartKrome protective plating for enhanced durability and corrosion resistance. Organized in an impact-resistant tool case, the master set includes 60 most frequently used star bit sockets: (14) external star sockets: 1/4-in drive: E4, E5, E6, E7, E8, 3/8-in drive: E10, E11, E12, E14, E16, 1/2-in drive: E18, E20, E22, E24; (17) star bit sockets:1/4-in drive: T6, T7, T8, T9, T10, T15, T20, T25, T27, T30, 3/8-in drive: T40, T45, T47, T50, T55, 1/2-in drive: T60, T70; (17) tamper proof star bit sockets: 1/4-in Drive: T6H, T7H, T8H, T9H, T10H, T15H, T20H, T25H, T27H, T30H, 3/8-in Drive: T40H, T45H, T47H, T50H, T55H, 1/2-in Drive: T60H, T70H; (12) star plus bit sockets: 1/4-in Drive: TP8, TP10, TP15, TP20, TP25, TP27, TP30, 3/8-in Drive: TP40, TP45, TP47, TP50, TP55, and 1/2-in Drive: TP60.

description: These 3 must-have tools make Cricut Joy™ projects even easier. The Spatula lets you carefully lift materials from your cutting mat that require a delicate touch, like paper and Infusible Ink™ Transfer Sheets. Use the Scraper to smooth out vinyl decals and remove scraps from your cutting mat when you're finished. features: Power Boil on Tri- and Dual-Ring Elements - this cooktop has a 3,000W tri-ring element and a 2,400W dual-ring element that allow for different pan sizes to be used for rapid boiling,Precision Temperature Control - set your burner to an exact degree, not just high, medium or low, using a smart pan, the cooktop maintains a specific temperature – from 100 to 500 degrees; perfect for sauces, candies and frying,Guided Cooking - connect a smart pan to your cooktop and your burners will adjust time and temperature based on a video-guided recipe in the app; choose from thousands of recipes and get perfectly cooked food (Pan sold separately),Glide Touch Controls - choose from 11 different heat settings with one easy swipe for total heat control,Easy Clean Surface - a smooth glass surface and glide touch controls makes cleaning up messes simpler than ever on this easy clean electric cooktop,Smart Cookware Rebate - smart pans and a wireless sous vide probe easily pair with this smart cooktop to ensure you get the perfect cooking results; earn a rebate for a free 11-in Hestan Cue Smart Pan,Built-in WiFi - this smart cooktop features Built-In WiFi so you can monitor your burners and view power levels, precision temperature, or on/off,Synchronized Elements - connect and control two cooktop burners as one to create a bigger cooking surface for pans such as griddles,Synchronized Fan and Lights - synchronize your cooktop and GE Profile over-the-range microwave or hood so that your fan or hood and lights automatically come on when a burner is activated with Chef Connect

description: Weeding and applying all types of vinyl is a breeze with these five essential vinyl  tools. This specialty set includes 5 specialty tools to help you weed and apply designs with speed, ease, and accuracy. Fine-Point Tweezers with long tips hold and lift slender, delicate vinyl strips with precision. Remove larger pieces with Hook Tweezers. Tackle weeding with the classic Weeder’s versatile angled tip. Pierce and lift or place cuts with the Piercing Tool. The hooked end of the Hook Weeder provides the ideal angle for even your most complex projects. Now you have a tool for every task, any vinyl, and your most detailed designs. For best results, use Cricut® Vinyl.

description: Get rid of food waste in a flash with the KRAUS WasteGuard Garbage Disposal. Featuring a 3800 RPM 1 Horsepower permanent-magnet motor, this disposal provides instant power to get rid of the toughest food scraps fast, with motor-saving shut-off technology that helps prevent damage in the event of a blockage. The continuous-feed design can shred large quantities of food scraps at once, and the grind chamber is encased in an insulated housing for quieter operation. Mounting is simple with an EZLock assembly that locks into place with a turn of the hand. Kit includes power cord and flange and stopper.
descriptionHtml: Get rid of food waste in a flash with the KRAUS WasteGuard Garbage Disposal. Featuring a 3800 RPM 1 Horsepower permanent-magnet motor, this disposal provides instant power to get rid of the toughest food scraps fast, with motor-saving shut-off technology that helps prevent damage in the event of a blockage. The continuous-feed design can shred large quantities of food scraps at once, and the grind chamber is encased in an insulated housing for quieter operation. Mounting is simple with an EZLock assembly that locks into place with a turn of the hand. Kit includes power cord and flange and stopper.
features: Powerful grinding of the toughest food scraps with superior 3800 RPM TO 1 HP ratio that eliminates waste in seconds,Easy-install EZLock mounting assembly with mounting flange locks into place with no plumber’s putty needed,Dimensions 8-5/8 in L x 10-3/4 in W x 16-1/8 in H; grinding chamber 40.6 oz; works with 3-1/2 in drain and 1-1/2 in plumbing,Installation-ready kit: 1 HP garbage disposal, drain and dishwasher connector, mounting flange with stainless steel rim, drain stopper/waste plunger for stubborn food scraps, pre-installed power cord, rubber gaskets for a perfect seal,Heavy-duty MagnaGrind permanent-magnet motor provides instant power to the grinder for faster operation than induction motors which take time to reach optimal speed; motor-saving shut off stops power in the event of a blockage to help prevent damage,Quiet and reliable operation with QuietStorm soundproofing technology and anti-vibration mounting system, with solid stainless steel components encased in ABS thermoplastic housing for a durable design that fits seamlessly into your kitchen,Continuous feed disposal is activated via wall switch or air switch, allowing you to shred large quantities of waste continuously for faster and easier operation than batch-feed disposals; slide food scraps into the drain and watch them disappear,Eco-friendly product cuts down on plastic garbage bag use, grinds up and condenses food scraps for quicker breakdown; septic safe with most septic systems in accordance with manufacturer guidelines (note: some foods are not compatible with septic),Universal design works with kitchen sinks with standard round 3-1/2-in drain opening and 1-1/2-in standard kitchen plumbing connections; certifications cUPC, ETL, and ISTA

description: Turn your inspiration board intentions into action with a little help from your DIY best friend, Cricut Joy™. Ridiculously easy to set up and use, this smart little cutting and writing machine helps you make more in less time, so you'll find yourself personalizing, organizing, and customizing every single day. With a plethora of projects that take just 15 minutes, Cricut Joy makes it fast and easy to make something unique for you – or anyone – at a moment's notice. It's the perfect companion to full-size Cricut Maker® and Cricut Explore® machines.

description: Summit's collection of electric cooktops offers the perfect fit and finish for a variety of kitchen spaces. Sized at a traditional 30" wide, the CR430SS is a 230V cooktop with four coil elements. The convenient layout puts a large 1800W burner in the front right side and rear left side, with two standard 1200W elements ensuring the perfect setup to cook multiple dishes with efficiency. Each burner includes a removable chrome drip bowl for easy cleanup. The CR430SS comes in a stainless steel finish, ideal for matching any home or hotel kitchen style. The push-to-turn knobs are centrally located for easy and safer use, eliminating any need to reach over hot burners to adjust the temperature. Indicator lights help to identify which burners are in use. Designed to fit standard cutouts, the CR430SS is designed for professional installation and does not include a cord. With its attractive style and user-friendly layout, this is the perfect cooktop for completing your kitchen at a friendly price.

description: Few things are as aggravating as reaching into a tight space with a ratchet and not having space to loosen or tighten the chosen fastener. Kobalt's 10-piece Drive Accessory Set was designed to assist in spanning the distance between your ratchet and that fastener. This set includes 1-1/2, 3, 6, and 10-inch extensions for 3/8-inch drive sockets and multiple adapters and universal joint extensions. Each extension is knurled on the shaft to give you a secure grip when using them to hand start nuts and bolts. Each extension, adapter and universal joint extension is made of strong and resilient chrome vanadium steel with a polished chrome finish for a lifetime of use. Adapter and extension sizes are listed below.

description: The Capri Tools ADVANCED SERIES sockets and bit sockets are made for the most demanding professionals. Crafted from custom forged premium steel, they undergo proprietary heat treatment and are precisely machined to perform in the toughest situations. The bits are forged with premium S2 steel. These S2 steel bits are exceptionally strong and durable; they withstand high torque and do not twist, protecting both the bit and the fastener. The largest 1/2-in drive hex bits (9/16-in/14 mm and above) are forged with custom Chrome Vanadium steel, giving these large bits balanced tensile strength for optimal performance. Our proprietary advanced heat treatment process further enhances the properties of the S2 and Chrome Vanadium steel alloy to achieve the optimal balance of strength and performance. Every hex bit is made true-to-size for the entire length, letting you use the full length of the bit. All bits have chamfered end to ensure a smooth fit onto fasteners. The sockets are made from premium Chrome Vanadium steel, plated with our SmartKrome protective plating for enhanced durability and corrosion resistance. Organized in an impact-resistant tool case, the set includes 32 most frequently used hex bit sockets: 1/4-in drive: 2, 2.5, 3, 4, 5, 5.5, 6 mm; 3/8-in drive: 7, 8, 9, 10 mm; 1/2-in drive: 12, 14, 15, 17, 19 mm; 1/4-in drive: 5/64, 3/32, 1/8, 5/32, 3/16, 7/32, 1/4-in; 3/8-in drive: 9/32, 5/16, 3/8-in; 1/2-in drive: 7/16, 1/2, 9/16, 5/8, 11/16, 3/4-in

description: From innovative faucets to kitchen sinks, you depend on Moen's thoughtful design. You can expect the same performance under the sink with our portfolio of garbage disposals. The Prep™ is designed for those who slice, dice and peel as part of basic meal prep, and need a little more help with clean up.  Featuring FAST TRACK enhanced features for a quicker installation for the Pro and DIY'er alike. Built for superior performance, they feature a VORTEX permanent magnet motor to finely grind food waste and help reduce jamming. The pre-installed power cord and Universal Xpress Mount system simplify installation. Professional home replacement service is included in each model's limited in-home warranty, guaranteeing help is there when you need it.

description: The V-Series 12PC. 3/8" Drive SAE Deep 6-Point Socket Set delivers unprecendented performance to the Craftsman brand. Engineered for professionals, this socket set features a magnetic socket rail for easy socket storage and organization. The sockets have premium features such as the 6-Point Socket Geometry that maximizes torque onto the flats of fasteners with an off-corner design. Other features include a chamfered and tapered tip design, which provides users with quicker socket-to-fastener engagement.  Backed by Craftsman's Lifetime Warranty, this product is designed to deliver the quality and durability expected from the Craftsman brand. If the product fails to perform for any reason, we will replace it. Return damaged product to a stocking Retail Partner or call 1-888-331-4569 for details. No proof of purchase required.

description: The KRAUS Kore Garbage Disposal is perfect for homeowners who use their kitchen regularly and want to keep cleanup simple. The heavy-duty high speed 3800 RPM 3/4 Horsepower motor provides instant power for fast and reliable grinding of food waste. The continuous-feed disposal grinds waste into small particles, helping reduce the amount of food waste and garbage bags going to landfills. Built with stainless steel components and ABS housing for lasting quality. Motor-saving shut-off technology helps prevent damage in case of blockage. QuietStorm soundproofing technology and anti-vibration mounting system help ensure quiet operation. The 3-bolt mounting system matches most standard flanges so you can easily replace your old disposal. Includes power cord, flange, and stopper.
descriptionHtml: The KRAUS Kore Garbage Disposal is perfect for homeowners who use their kitchen regularly and want to keep cleanup simple. The heavy-duty high speed 3800 RPM 3/4 Horsepower motor provides instant power for fast and reliable grinding of food waste. The continuous-feed disposal grinds waste into small particles, helping reduce the amount of food waste and garbage bags going to landfills. Built with stainless steel components and ABS housing for lasting quality. Motor-saving shut-off technology helps prevent damage in case of blockage. The 3-bolt mounting system matches most standard flanges so you can easily replace your old disposal. Includes power cord, flange, and stopper.
features: Fast and reliable grinding of the toughest food scraps with 3800 RPM TO 3/4 HP ratio that eliminates waste in seconds,8-5/8 in W x 15-1/4 in H; 10-5/8 min install clearance; grinding chamber 40.6 oz; fits 3-1/2 in drain and 1-1/2 in plumbing,Universal 3-bolt mounting system matches standard garbage disposal flanges for easy replacement of your old disposal,Installation-ready kit: 3/4 HP garbage disposal, drain and dishwasher connector, removable splash guard, mounting flange with stainless steel rim, drain stopper/waste plunger, pre-installed power cord, rubber gaskets for a perfect seal,High-speed MagnaGrind permanent-magnet motor provides instant power to the grinder for faster operation than induction motors which take time to reach optimal speed; motor-saving shut off stops power in the event of a blockage to help prevent damage,Quiet and reliable operation with QuietStorm soundproofing technology and anti-vibration mounting system, with solid stainless steel components encased in ABS thermoplastic housing for a durable design that fits seamlessly into your kitchen,Powerful continuous feed disposal activated via wall switch or air switch, allowing you to shred large quantities of waste continuously for faster and easier operation than batch-feed disposals; slide food scraps into the drain and watch them disappear,Eco-friendly product cuts down on plastic garbage bag use, grinds up and condenses food scraps for quicker breakdown; septic safe with most septic systems in accordance with manufacturer guidelines (note: some foods are not compatible with septic),Universal design works with kitchen sinks with standard round 3-1/2” drain opening and 1-1/2” standard kitchen plumbing connections; 5-year limited warranty and top-rated customer service available to support your needs; certifications cUPC, ETL, and ISTA
name: Kraus Kore Corded 3/4-HP Continuous Feed Noise Insulation Garbage Disposal

The premium quality universal 35-foot Prolux hose can withstand heavy abuse and can not be crushed beyond use. This crush-proof hose is lightweight and offers superior durability. A comfortable handle with a 3-way switch allows you absolute control of the entire system from anywhere. The handle switch can turn the unit on and off and has the ability to control the power nozzle separately. Switching between carpeted and hard floor surfaces is quick and simple. Wessel Werk makes one of the highest quality and durable power nozzles on the market. The EBK 360 offers many features and conveniences. Some of the features include: soft rubber bumper and wheels to protect floors and furniture from damage, head height adjustment to ensure the perfect brush roll level for any surface and long-lasting LED headlights perfect for dim areas.

description: The Capri Tools 88-Piece Master Bit Socket Set is a complete collection of most frequently used bit sockets. We use premium S2 steel tempered with our proprietary heat treatment process to make these bits (other than 1/2-in drive hex bits 9/16-in/14 mm and above). They are exceptionally durable and strong, withstand high torque and do not twist, protecting both the bit and the fastener. The 1/2-in drive hex bits 9/16-in/14 mm and above are forged with our custom Chrome Vanadium steel, giving them a balance tensile strength for optimal performance. The sockets are constructed with premium Chrome Vanadium steel and plated with our own SmartKrome protective plating - durable and resist corrosion. We made all of our hex bits true-to-size for their entire length, letting you use the full length of the hex bit. Chamfered end ensures a smooth fit onto fasteners. Meets and exceeds ASME B107.110 standards. This master set includes: (13) external star sockets: 1/4-in drive: E4, E5, E6, E7, E8, 3/8-in drive: E10, E12, E14, E16, 1/2-in drive: E18, E20, E22, E24; (15) star bit sockets:1/4-in drive: T6, T7, T8, T9, T10, T15, T20, T25, T27, T30, 3/8-in drive: T40, T45, T50, 1/2-in drive: T55, T60; (15) long star bit sockets: 1/4-in drive (3-1/16-in long bit): T6, T7, T8, T9, T10, T15, T20, T25, T27, T30, 3/8-in drive (2-3/4-in long bit): T40, T45, T50, 1/2-in drive (2-1/2-in long bit): T55, T60; (16) hex bit sockets in metric: 1/4-in drive: 2, 2.5, 3, 4, 5, 6 mm, 3/8-in drive: 6, 7, 8, 9, 10 mm, 1/2-in drive: 10, 12, 14, 17, 19 mm; (7) long hex bit sockets in metric: 1/4-in drive (3-1/16-in long bit): 4, 5, 6 mm, 3/8-in drive (2-3/4-in long bit): 7, 8, 9, 10 mm; (15) hex bit sockets in SAE: 1/4-in drive: 1/8, 9/64, 5/32, 3/16, 7/32, 1/4 in, 3/8-in drive: 7/32, 1/4, 5/16, 3/8 in; 7/16, 1/2, 9/16, 5/8, 3/4-in, 1/2-in drive: 7/16, 1/2, 9/16, 5/8, 3/4-in; (7) long hex bit sockets in SAE: 1/4-in drive (3-1/16-in long bit): 1/8, 5/32, 3/16-in; 3/8-in drive (2-3/4-in long bit): 7/32, 1/4

description: Looking for stunning and dramatic? Only from Cricut®. Everyday Iron-On™ with StrongBond™ outlasts 50+ washes and is compatible with a huge breadth of base materials, including wood! Use your Cricut machine to cut complex designs and you’ll weed with ease for a flawless application. From terrific T-shirts to heartwarming home decor, amazing accessories to handmade presents, this heat transfer material is your go-to for almost any iron-on idea. Use a single color or layer up to three to create one-of-a-kind patterns and projects. Use with all Cricut cutting machines. For a flawless iron-on application, use Cricut EasyPress®. Or apply with household iron. Care Instructions Allow 24 hours after application before washing. Wash and tumble dry inside out. Do not bleach. If you need to iron, only iron on the backside of the garment.

description: Upgrade your kitchen with the FOTILE 12 Inch Electric Cooktop, EEG30101, featuring a powerful 2400W output. This cooktop contains coiled metal elements underneath tempered ceramic glass, electronically heated to your desired temperature. The coil then heats the ceramic surface, providing even heat distribution to your cookware. Compatible with almost all types of cookware, this cooktop is a versatile addition to any kitchen. Enjoy worry-free cooking with overheat protection, automatic pan detection, and child safety locks. Upgrade your cooking experience with the FOTILE 12 Inch Electric Cooktop for safe and efficient cooking.
descriptionHtml: Upgrade your kitchen with the FOTILE 12 Inch Electric Cooktop, EEG30101, featuring a powerful 2400W output. This cooktop contains coiled metal elements underneath tempered ceramic glass, electronically heated to your desired temperature. The coil then heats the ceramic surface, providing even heat distribution to your cookware. Compatible with almost all types of cookware, this cooktop is a versatile addition to any kitchen. Enjoy worry-free cooking with overheat protection, automatic pan detection, and child safety locks. Upgrade your cooking experience with the FOTILE 12 Inch Electric Cooktop for safe and efficient cooking.
features: Featuring both single and dual ring control. With 9 levels of power and a max temperature of 1004°F, it offers precise temperature control for efficient cooking. Prepare delicious meals with ease on this versatile cooktop,Operates quietly with its fan-less design, providing a more peaceful cooking experience. The cooktop also features strong convection for natural cool down, ensuring efficient heat dissipation and longer lifespan,With a convenient 99-minute timer, making it easy to keep track of cooking times and ensure that your meals are prepared to perfection. This feature offers added convenience and helps to prevent overcooking or undercooking your food,Features with a warning system that alerts users to residual heat on the surface. When the temperature is above 131 °F, the "H" light will turn on, and when it's lower than 113 °F, it will turn off, ensuring safe and worry-free cooking,Residual Heat Technology for Energy Efficiency: EEG30101 uses advanced residual heat technology to keep your food warm while minimizing energy usage, so you can cook with confidence and reduce your carbon footprint,Features with surface temperature protection with a maximum temperature limit of 1004 °F to prevent damage to the surface or cookware. The cooktop will automatically shut off if the temperature limit is reached, ensuring safe and worry-free cooking,Features with an auto-shutoff protection mechanism that powers off the cooktop after two hours of inactivity, ensuring safety and preventing energy waste. Please note that this feature does not apply to the timer mode,Mechanical control for precise and reliable temperature adjustments,Features with a convenient Circle Touch Control that allows you to adjust the output power and set the timer with ease. With its user-friendly interface and sleek design, this cooktop offers a modern and efficient way to cook your favorite meals
name: FOTILE 12-in 1 Burner Smooth Surface (Radiant) Black Electric Cooktop

description: The InSinkErator Evolution 45SS 3/4 HP Garbage Disposal offers a hygienic, convenient and environmentally responsible way to rid your kitchen of food scraps. Septic-safe for properly maintained septic systems, this compact garbage disposal quickly grinds food waste into tiny particles that easily flush down the kitchen drain. Part of the InSinkErator Advanced Series, premium InSinkErator garbage disposals with patented SoundSeal technology for quieter operation than standard disposals, plus superior grind performance for tough and fibrous food scraps, the Evolution 45SS has a 3/4 HP, heavy-duty Dura-Drive induction motor. It provides jam-busting torque with stainless steel grind components in a compact design that fits under the kitchen sink. This EZ Connect InSinkErator garbage disposal also has an EZ Connect Hardwire Adapter, EZ Grip Handles, EZ Removable Dishwasher Inlet Plug, and Lift and Latch technology for easy installation. Since 1938, InSinkErator helps you Kitchen Better.

description: The InSinkErator Evolution 55SS 1 HP Garbage Disposal offers a hygienic, convenient and environmentally responsible way to rid your kitchen of food scraps. Septic-safe for properly maintained septic systems, this compact garbage disposal grinds food waste into tiny particles that flush down the kitchen drain. Part of the InSinkErator Advanced Series, premium InSinkErator garbage disposals with quieter operation than standard disposals and superior grind performance to handle tough and fibrous food scraps, the 55SS disposal features a 1 HP, heavy-duty Dura-Drive induction motor. Its jam-busting torque and rust-resistant, stainless steel grind components are packed into the quietest, compact design that fits easily under the kitchen sink. This EZ Connect InSinkErator garbage disposal also has an EZ Connect Hardwire Adapter, EZ Grip Handles, EZ Removable Dishwasher Inlet Plug, and Lift and Latch technology for easy installation. Since 1938, InSinkErator helps you Kitchen Better.

description:
Summit's line of all-in-one combination kitchenettes brings complete kitchen convenience in a slim-fitting design. These units come fully featured with everything you need for the home foodservice experience, including a refrigerator with a freezer compartment, 4-burner gas range with oven, sink with faucet, cutlery bin with a removable cutting board cover, and storage cabinet for dry goods. 

The ACK63GASBSS is a 63" wide kitchenette with an easy-fitting 24" depth. This unit comes with a stainless steel countertop offering durability in a professional look. The surface includes a small cutlery bin, with a removable cutting board cover to ensure easy food prep. The compact sink features a ready-to-use faucet. Underneath the sink is a large cabinet with a removable shelf for added storage convenience.

Unlike many other brands' kitchenettes, all Summit units include a refrigerator with a freezer compartment to cover all of your cold storage needs. The ACK63GASB includes the two-door, ENERGY STAR certified CP34BSS, with 3.2 cu.ft. of storage space. A dual evaporator system separately cools the auto defrost refrigerator section and manual defrost freezer compartment for improved overall performance. This model also includes an adjustable glass shelf, door storage, and a crisper. The ACK63GASB also ships with Summit PRO247SS, a 24" wide stainless steel gas range complete with 4 sealed burners with continuous cast iron grates and a full oven compartment with a bake and broil function. This range includes low and high output burners to meet all your cooking needs, adjustable slide-out racks, and is LP convertible aftermarket with included kit. The range can be installed on the left or right side of the kitchenette.

description: Keep your wine perfectly chilled in the Maxximum 24" Dual Zone Wine Cooler. This 46-bottle capacity wine fridge is ideal for the living room, office, man cave, she shed, bar, basement or anywhere you want to store and preserve your wine collection beautifully. Easily view your wine choices through the glass door. This compact wine cooler features dual temperature zones with a temperature range of 34°F to 65°F. This dual zone wine refrigerator includes six wine rack inserts to hold your bottles. The door is reversible, making it ideal for any space. The user friendly electronic control with LED display lets you easily monitor your collection. This two-zone wine cooler measures 25.25" x 23.88" x 34.75" and can be freestanding or built-in. Store and preserve your wine at optimal temperatures with the Maxximum 24" Dual Zone Wine Cooler. Covered by the Maxximum One-Year Limited Warranty.

description: Everyone deserves to get the most out of their wine. With the right storage, wine’s complexities come to life. description: Cut, draw, score, and more with the DIY dream machine—now smarter and faster than ever. From vinyl, iron-on, cardstock, and specialty materials like bonded fabric and cork, Cricut Explore® 3 works with 100+ materials, bringing incredible speed and precision to every project. description:
UMMIT brings innovative value into the kitchen with all-in-one combination units for full-service use. Our ACKSPWD series features a full-sized refrigerator-freezer, washer/dryer combo, 2-burner cooktop, sink, and storage cabinet to create a complete one-wall kitchenette. 

Model ACKSPWD861G is comprised of three pieces: our North American made frost-free FF1427W refrigerator-freezer; our C60ELGLASS kitchenette with sink, cabinets, and cooktop; and our SPWD2202W 24" non-vented washer/dryer combo. The exterior features a clean white finish, with stainless steel accents on the kitchenette work surface and dishwasher handle to elevate your kitchen style.

The FF1427W refrigerator offers nearly 13 cu.ft. of storage capacity. Frost-free operation ensures minimum user maintenance. The refrigerator section includes adjustable glass shelves, a large crisper drawer, and door storage, while the large freezer includes a removable shelf and door rack. This unit has a user-reversible door swing and can be installed to the left or right of your kitchenette. 

The C60ELGLASS kitchenette includes a 2-burner radiant cooktop in black glass with a pre-installed 115V 3-prong power cord for easy setup. Two storage cabinet include removable shelves ideal for holding pantry items, cleaning supplies, and more. The ACKSPWD861G ships with our SPWD2202W all-in-one washer/dryer combo, a non-vented 115V unit to meet all of your laundry needs. The washer/dryer features 16 wash cycles with a combination of dial and digital controls for intuitive use. The stainless steel interior drum offers durable use to hold up load after load.
