description: Meet Cricut Maker, the ultimate smart cutting machine. With the ability to use more advanced tools, Cricut Maker gives you the freedom to make virtually any DIY project you can imagine, from 3D art to home decor, jewelry, iron-on, vinyl, paper projects, and so much more. It has the tools to cut hundreds of materials quickly and accurately, from the most delicate paper and fabric to the tough stuff like matboard, leather, and basswood. Use the Rotary Blade to cut fabric for a sewing project — without backing material. Switch to Knife Blade (sold separately) and cut thicker and denser materials for added dimension and depth. Or quickly switch between scoring, engraving, debossing, and other decorative effects with a variety of specialty tips (sold separately). Featuring unique cutting versatility, a huge library of design ideas, sewing patterns available instantly, and easy-to-use apps, Cricut Maker delivers professional-level cutting performance that anyone can use.

description: This spectrum of six shades will brighten every day with creative possibility. Only from Cricut®. Everyday Iron-On™ with StrongBond™ Guarantee outlasts 50+ washes and is compatible with a huge breadth of base materials, including wood! Use your Cricut machine to cut complex designs and you’ll weed with ease for a flawless application. From terrific T-shirts to heartwarming home decor, amazing accessories to handmade presents, this heat transfer material is your go-to for almost any iron-on idea. Use a single color or layer up to three to create one-of-a-kind patterns and projects. Use with all Cricut cutting machines. For a flawless iron-on application, use Cricut EasyPress®. Or apply with household iron. Care Instructions Allow 24 hours after application before washing. Wash and tumble dry inside out. Do not bleach. If you need to iron, only iron on the backside of the garment

The ACK72COILW is a 72" wide kitchenette with an easy-fitting 24" depth. This unit comes with a stainless steel countertop offering durability in a professional look. The surface includes a small cutlery bin, with a removable cutting board cover to ensure easy food prep. The compact sink features a ready-to-use faucet. Underneath the sink is a large cabinet with a removable shelf for added storage convenience.

Unlike many other brands' kitchenettes, all Summit units include a refrigerator with a freezer compartment to cover all of your cold storage needs. description: This is your essential iron-on tool. Enjoy heat-transfer perfection every time. Cricut EasyPress® 2 combines the speed of a heat press and the convenience of a household iron. Eliminate guesswork and get fast, effortless results that really last – even after repeated washes! Just enter the recommended time and temperature settings, apply heat, and when the beep sounds, you’re done! Its ceramic-coated heat plate is adjustable up to 400F (205C). You'll love the safety features, including an insulated Safety Base and auto-shutoff feature. Plus it's super lightweight, unbelievably portable, easy to store, and compatible with all Infusible Ink™ products and most major brands of heat-transfer vinyl material. And of course, it's a perfect complement to Cricut® cutting machines.

description: Premium Vinyl - Removable works fabulously with the widest variety of base materials, including wood, metal, and more! Whether you’re new to the Cricut family or have been creating with our products for years, you’ll find it easy to bring your artistic vision to life with our removable adhesive vinyl in hand. With a few simple steps, create your own intricate designs with your Cricut machine and weed with ease to prep for flawless application. Create a custom decal, design heartwarming home decor, embellish accessories with one-of-a-kind designs, and create handmade gifts that will leave a lasting impression. Premium Vinyl works with all Cricut cutting machines. This quality vinyl lies flat without tunneling or bubbling to give you a flawless cut every time. When applied correctly, Premium Vinyl - Removable can be removed without leaving any residue! Pick out your favorite Premium Vinyl - Removable colors today!

description: COMFEE’s countertop dishwasher can meet all your daily cleaning needs, with a huge capacity of 6 place settings. It has over 8 functions, including Heavy, Normal, Baby-Care, ECO, Glass, Speed, Rinse, and Mini-Party, helping with the extra-drying function. Our mini dishwasher can be installed easily with accessories and simple plumbing connection steps like other full-size dishwashers. Also, it can be connected to the faucet directly (A suitable adaptor is needed). It can be flexibly placed on the table or fitted in the cupboard, depending on your needs.
descriptionHtml: COMFEE’s countertop dishwasher can meet all your daily cleaning needs, with a huge capacity of 6 place settings. It has over 8 functions, including Heavy, Normal, Baby-Care, ECO, Glass, Speed, Rinse, and Mini-Party, helping with the extra-drying function. Our mini dishwasher can be installed easily with accessories and simple plumbing connection steps like other full-size dishwashers. Also, it can be connected to the faucet directly (A suitable adaptor is needed). It can be flexibly placed on the table or fitted in the cupboard, depending on your needs.
features: Wash your favorite dishware and glass meticulously with a lower wash temperature.,A perfect size (H17.2″×W20.6″×D21.6″) for 2-3 people, COMFEE’ compact dishwasher is suitable for dorms, RVs, and apartments.,Most of the cleaning cycles, including Heavy, Normal, Baby-Care, ECO, Glass help give extra clean dishes,Heavily soiled dishes are cleaned with 12 washing nozzles, accompanied with 360° spiral spray wash to ensure complete washing.,Accompanied with Energy Star compliance, water consumption can be as low as 2.77 gallons of water, which greatly saves your costs.,Highly effective for cleaning the heaviest soiled dishware and other utensils, delivering you clean and hygienic tableware.,Child safety lock to protect your children from unexpected accidents.,Please reference Product Guide and User Manual for more information,1-Year Warranty :  1-Year limited manufacturer warranty
name: Comfee 21.6-in Portable Countertop Dishwasher (White) ENERGY STAR, 49-dBA

description:
SUMMIT brings innovative value into the kitchen with all-in-one combination units for full-service use. Our ACKSPWD series features a full-sized refrigerator-freezer, washer/dryer combo, 2-burner cooktop, sink, and storage cabinet to create a complete one-wall kitchenette. 

Model ACKSPWD86 is comprised of three pieces: our North American made frost-free FF1427W refrigerator-freezer; our C60EL kitchenette with sink, cabinets, and cooktop; and our SPWD2202W 24" non-vented washer/dryer combo. The exterior features a clean white finish, with stainless steel accents on the kitchenette work surface and dishwasher handle to elevate your kitchen style.

The FF1427W refrigerator offers nearly 13 cu.ft. of storage capacity. Frost-free operation ensures minimum user maintenance. The refrigerator section includes adjustable glass shelves, a large crisper drawer, and door storage, while the large freezer includes a removable shelf and door rack. This unit has a user-reversible door swing and can be installed to the left or right of your kitchenette. 

The C60EL kitchenette includes a 2-burner coil cooktop with a pre-installed 115V 3-prong power cord for easy setup. The stainless steel sink features a hot and cold water faucet. Two storage cabinet include removable shelves ideal for holding pantry items, cleaning supplies, and more. The ACKSPWD86 ships with our SPWD2202W all-in-one washer/dryer combo, a non-vented 115V unit to meet all of your laundry needs. The washer/dryer features 16 wash cycles with a combination of dial and digital controls for intuitive use. The stainless steel interior drum offers durable use to hold up load after load.

description: The Quiet Glide rolling ladder is a classy way to add functionality to your library, closet, wine cellar, kitchens, pantries or lofts, anywhere you want to reach those out-of-the-way places. With the Quiet Glide rolling library ladder, it is all about choice. Quiet Glide provides rolling library ladder hardware kits, rail kits and wood ladder kits. Our rolling library ladder hardware kits come in four finishes, three types of upper guides and three styles of ladder wheels. Our unique ladder rail system is the only library ladder rail kit on the market that offers solid aluminum rails - not hollow tubes. All the parts on a Quiet Glide rolling library ladder are machined or manufactured by American Craftsman. Our installation guide will help you choose the design and products for your application.

description:
Summit's line of all-in-one combination kitchenettes brings complete kitchen convenience in a slim-fitting design. These units come fully featured with everything you need for the home foodservice experience, including a refrigerator with a freezer compartment, 4-burner smooth top range with oven, sink with faucet, cutlery bin with a removable cutting board cover, and storage cabinet for dry goods. 

The ACK72ELSTW is a 54" wide kitchenette with an easy-fitting 24.25" depth. This unit comes with a stainless steel countertop offering durability in a professional look. The surface includes a small cutlery bin, with a removable cutting board cover to ensure easy food prep. The compact sink features a ready-to-use faucet. Underneath the sink is a large cabinet with a removable shelf for added storage convenience.

Unlike many other brands' kitchenettes, all Summit units include a refrigerator with a freezer compartment to cover all of your cold storage needs. The ACK72ELSTW includes the CT661W, with 5.1 cu.ft. of storage space. A dual evaporator system separately cools the auto defrost refrigerator section and manual defrost freezer compartment for improved overall performance. This model includes adjustable glass shelves, door storage, a scalloped wine shelf, and crisper. The ACK72ELSTW also ships with Summit REX2421WRT, a 24" wide 220V electric range complete with a smooth-top 4-element cooking surface and a full oven compartment with a bake and broil function. This range includes a large window with interior oven light, adjustable slide-out oven racks, hot surface indicator lights for added safety, and a pull-out drawer for storage as needed. The range can be installed on the left or right side of the kitchenette.

description: It's easy as ever to cut straight lines with the 13 in (33 cm) Cricut® Portable Trimmer. The unique, easy-glide blade system leaves precise, straight cuts. An ergonomic, custom-fit handle provides a smooth grip cut after cut. The dual-hinged rail makes it a cinch to load and measure materials, and cut from both sides. It features measuring marks and rulers in both inches and centimeters, 1/4 in (0.3 cm) grid marks, and a 16 in (40 cm) swing-out arm help you accurately measure every cut. A convenient storage compartment on the underside keeps your replacement blade handy.

description: DIY stenciled walls, tables, and more are just a cut, paint, and peel away. Cricut® Smart Stencil™ loads into your compatible Cricut cutting machine for precise cuts, without a mat. This stencil film has an adhesive backing for easy application — it’s durable, yet removes without residue. It works with numerous paint applications and is versatile enough for both curved and flat surfaces including walls, wood, glass, canvas, and beyond. A single stencil cuts up to 12 ft (3.6 m) with ease. For use with Cricut Explore® 3 and Cricut Maker® 3.

description: The Quiet Glide rolling ladder is a classy way to add functionality to your library, closet, wine cellar, kitchens, pantries or lofts, anywhere you want to reach those out-of-the-way places. With the Quiet Glide rolling library ladder, it is all about choice. Quiet Glide provides rolling library ladder hardware kits, rail kits and wood ladder kits. Our rolling library ladder hardware kits come in four finishes, three types of upper guides and three styles of ladder wheels. Our unique ladder rail system is the only library ladder rail kit on the market that offers solid aluminum rails - not hollow tubes. All the parts on a Quiet Glide rolling library ladder are machined or manufactured by American Craftsman. Our installation guide will help you choose the design and products for your application.

description:
SUMMIT brings innovative value into the kitchen with all-in-one combination units for full-service use. Our ACKDW series features a full-sized refrigerator-freezer, dishwasher, 2-burner cooktop, sink, and storage cabinet to create a complete one-wall kitchenette. 

Model ACKDW72 is comprised of three pieces: our North American made frost-free FF946W refrigerator-freezer; our C48EL kitchenette with sink, cabinet, and cooktop; and our DW242WADA 24" dishwasher. The exterior features a clean white finish, with stainless steel accents on the kitchenette work surface and dishwasher handle to elevate your kitchen style.

The FF946W refrigerator offers 8.8 cu.ft. of storage capacity. Frost-free operation ensures minimum user maintenance. The refrigerator section includes adjustable glass shelves, a large crisper drawer, and door storage, while the large freezer includes a removable shelf and door rack. This unit has a user-reversible door swing and can be installed to the left or right of your kitchenette. 

The C48EL kitchenette includes a 2-burner coil cooktop with a pre-installed 115V 3-prong power cord for easy setup. The stainless steel sink features a hot and cold water faucet. A large storage cabinet includes a removable shelf. The ACKDW72 ships with our European DW242WADA dishwasher, with an ENERGY STAR certified ultra quiet performance that runs at just 47 dB. This dishwasher is designed with a fully featured stainless steel interior for versatile loading. The intuitive top-located digital controls let you choose between 8 wash programs with 5 auxiliary functions, including a half-load setting for added water savings. The dishwasher also includes its own pre-installed 3-prong cord.

description:
Summit's line of all-in-one combination kitchenettes brings complete kitchen convenience in a slim-fitting design. These units come fully featured with everything you need for the home foodservice experience, including a refrigerator with a freezer compartment, 4-burner gas range with oven, sink with faucet, cutlery bin with a removable cutting board cover, and storage cabinet for dry goods. 

The ACK60GASW is a 60" wide kitchenette with an easy-fitting 24" depth. This unit comes with a stainless steel countertop offering durability in a professional look. The surface includes a small cutlery bin, with a removable cutting board cover to ensure easy food prep. The compact sink features a ready-to-use faucet. Underneath the sink is a large cabinet with a removable shelf for added storage convenience.

Unlike many other brands' kitchenettes, all Summit units include a refrigerator with a freezer compartment to cover all of your cold storage needs. The ACK60GASW includes the two-door, ENERGY STAR certified CP34W, with 3.2 cu.ft. of storage space. A dual evaporator system separately cools the auto defrost refrigerator section and manual defrost freezer compartment for improved overall performance. This model also includes an adjustable glass shelf, door storage, and a crisper. The ACK60GASW also ships with Summit RG200WS, a 20" wide 115V gas range complete with 4 sealed burners with continuous cast iron grates and a full oven compartment with a bake and broil function. This range includes low and high output burners to meet all your cooking needs, adjustable slide-out racks, and is LP convertible aftermarket with included kit. The range can be installed on the left or right side of the kitchenette.

description:
SUMMIT brings innovative value into the kitchen with all-in-one combination units for full-service use. Our ACKSPWD series features a full-sized refrigerator-freezer, washer/dryer combo, 2-burner cooktop, sink, and storage cabinet to create a complete one-wall kitchenette. 

Model ACKSPWD821G is comprised of three pieces: our North American made frost-free FF946W refrigerator-freezer; our C60ELGLASS kitchenette with sink, cabinets, and cooktop; and our SPWD2202W 24" non-vented washer/dryer combo. The exterior features a clean white finish, with stainless steel accents on the kitchenette work surface and dishwasher handle to elevate your kitchen style.

The FF946W refrigerator offers 8.8 cu.ft. of storage capacity. Frost-free operation ensures minimum user maintenance. The refrigerator section includes adjustable glass shelves, a large crisper drawer, and door storage, while the large freezer includes a removable shelf and door rack. This unit has a user-reversible door swing and can be installed to the left or right of your kitchenette. 

The C60ELGLASS kitchenette includes a 2-burner radiant cooktop in black glass with a pre-installed 115V 3-prong power cord for easy setup. The stainless steel sink features a hot and cold water faucet. Two storage cabinet include removable shelves ideal for holding pantry items, cleaning supplies, and more. The ACKSPWD821G ships with our SPWD2202W all-in-one washer/dryer combo, a non-vented 115V unit to meet all of your laundry needs. The washer/dryer features 16 wash cycles with a combination of dial and digital controls for intuitive use. The stainless steel interior drum offers durable use to hold up load after load.

description: The Frigidaire beverage cooler fits in small spaces easily, stores enough beverages for any occasion, and features adjustable thermostat settings for custom chilling. This mini beverage fridge chills down to 40 degrees Fahrenhent and has plenty of room for cans, bottles, and all your favorite snacks at the perfect temperature. Enhance any space, from your rec room, or dorm to your home bar or office with this stylish grey colored beverage center. The sleek glass door provides a view of the interior contents. Front leveling legs help to make sure that your unit is always level so that the cooler will run smoothly. Holds 10 bottles 750ml and 60 cans or 88 cans or 25 bottles 750ml.

description: Combining equal parts personality and functionality, this double-sided, self-healing cutting mat will inspire your creative imagination and provide the perfect cutting surface for all of your projects. With a delightfully decorative print on one side, you’ll love the splash of color it brings to your workspace, even when you’re not working. Keep your cuts clean and enjoy more creative cutting options with multi-angled grid lines. Extend your mat life with the extra-thick surface, which prevents blade cut-through. The 12" x 12" (30.5 cm x 30.5 cm) and 12" x 24" (30.5 cm 61 cm) reference marks match Cricut® machine mat sizes. Not for use in Cricut machines.

description: This countertop wine cellar is designed to be seen and not heard. The Newair Shadow-T Series 6 Bottle Thermoelectric Wine Fridge delivers the ultimate storage system for your collection, whether you’re new to wine or a lifelong connoisseur. Ultra-quiet thermoelectric cooling eliminates vibrations that can disturb sediment and destroy the delicate flavors of your wine. The sleek, compact design features a black mirrored glass door with a frameless design and hidden hinge. The triple-pane glass blocks harmful UV rays to protect your wine’s flavor and aroma while resisting smudges and fingerprints. This modern and durable wine mini fridge boasts a user-friendly control panel that is seamlessly built into the glass, making it effortless to select the perfect temperature for your reds, whites, and sparklers.

name: NewAir 13.6-in W Black Freestanding Wine Cooler

description: The Quiet Glide rolling ladder is a classy way to add functionality to your library, closet, wine cellar, kitchens, pantries or lofts, anywhere you want to reach those out-of-the-way places. With the Quiet Glide rolling library ladder, it is all about choice. Quiet Glide provides rolling library ladder hardware kits, rail kits and wood ladder kits. Our rolling library ladder hardware kits come in four finishes, three types of upper guides and three styles of ladder wheels. Our unique ladder rail system is the only library ladder rail kit on the market that offers solid aluminum rails - not hollow tubes. All the parts on a Quiet Glide rolling library ladder are machined or manufactured by American Craftsman. Our installation guide will help you choose the design and products for your application.

description: Easily install this convertible compactor to take care of the trash anywhere. With a portable design, it can even go in the garage or pantry. The generous 1.4 cu. ft. capacity holds more, so you can take the trash out less. Easy Rollers™ installation wheels help you position the compactor where you want it. Plus, the Touch-Toe™ provide hands-free opening. A light tap of the toe does the trick, releasing the drawer with ease. What's more, you get Touch Pad controls on the Clean Touch™ console. Its smooth surface has no dials or switches so it wipes down easily with the simple swipe of a cloth.

description: The American Standard Elite ASE-90, 3/4 HP stainless steel garbage disposal is designed to provide a premium experience from installation through your post-dinner cleanup. This disposal comes with a pre-connected power cord and universal 3-bolt mounting system to allow for quick and easy installation/replacement. Packed with features, this model has been fitted with full stainless steel grinding components, a balanced grind system for smooth grind with reduced vibration, and an anti-bacterial odor-reducing chamber. Backed by a 10-year warranty and lifetime corrosion warranty, this disposal is sure to keep your sink working great for years to come.

description: Start your creative journey with Cricut Maker, plus a selection of tools, materials, and more. Create virtually any project on your wish list with Cricut Maker – 3D art, home decor, jewelry, iron-on tees, paper projects and so much more. Cut 300+ materials quickly and accurately, from the most delicate paper and fabric to the tough stuff like matboard and leather. Use the Rotary Blade to cut fabric for a sewing project, or switch to Knife Blade to cut thicker and denser materials for added dimension and depth. description:
Summit's line of all-in-one combination kitchenettes brings complete kitchen convenience in a slim-fitting design. These units come fully featured with everything you need for the home foodservice experience, including a refrigerator with a freezer compartment, 4-element electric coil cooktop with oven, sink with faucet, cutlery bin with a removable cutting board cover, and storage cabinet for dry goods. 

The ACK54COILW is a 54" wide kitchenette with an easy-fitting 24" depth. This unit comes with a stainless steel countertop offering durability in a professional look. The surface includes a small cutlery bin, with a removable cutting board cover to ensure easy food prep. The compact sink features a ready-to-use faucet. Underneath the sink is a cabinet with a removable shelf for added storage convenience.

Unlike many other brands' kitchenettes, all Summit units include a refrigerator with a freezer compartment to cover all of your cold storage needs. The ACK54COILW includes the two-door, ENERGY STAR certified CP34W, with 3.2 cu.ft. of storage space. A dual evaporator system separately cools the auto defrost refrigerator section and manual defrost freezer compartment for improved overall performance. This model also includes an adjustable glass shelf, door storage, and a crisper. The ACK54COILW also ships with Summit RE2411W, a 24" wide 220V electric range complete with a 4-element coil cooking surface, and a full oven compartment with a bake and broil function. This range includes sensors on each element that cycle off if the temperature nears flashpoint for safer cooking, adjustable oven racks, indicator lights that illuminate when the elements and oven are in use, and a storage drawer for added convenience. The range can be installed on the left or right side of the kitchenette.

description: Versatility is just the beginning with so many Legacy desking options. This classic corner workstation has a curved center for a seamless transition between desk and return. On this Left Corner Credenza, the return attaches to the left hand side and it is not reversible. It comes with two box-file pedestals that each have one box drawer and one file drawer that accepts both letter and legal filing. All drawers lock and include ergonomically designed drawer pulls for convenience and ease in operation. Adjustable glides on the bottom of the base keep the desktop level and are easy to adjust. Wire management grommets keep cables clear of work areas. Finished in an stylish Ash Grey laminate, this desk coordinates with other Legacy furniture. The Legacy collection is constructed of a 1-inch thick thermal fused melamine laminate with a 3-millimeter commercial grade matching PVC edge. Laminates are scratch, stain and scald resistant. Legacy casegoods are backed by a 10-year limited manufacturer's warranty.

description: The XTERRA SB120 Recumbent Bike offers a smooth lower-body workout in a convenient step-through frame design for easy accessibility. The small footprint maximizes your use of space while providing a low-impact, heart-healthy workout. With 8 levels of on-demand resistance, riders of all types are sure to get a workout that is matched to their fitness level and desired intensity. Features like a padded seat with seat back, oversized adjustable foot pedals, and multi-grip padded handlebars allow you to focus more on your fitness goals knowing that you will be comfortable and secure. To keep you at the top of your training, the console features an easy-to-read LCD that displays your most important metrics to help you stay motivated. Built-in hand pulse grips on the handles next to the seat let you easily track your heart rate to ensure you get the results you want.

description: The Bush Furniture Cabot L Shaped Computer Desk offers a spacious and efficient workplace for your home or office. Enjoy a beautiful traditional look with smart features for your convenience. The L Shaped Desk design provides a large durable work surface and just the right amount of storage to keep you feeling neat and organized. Desk storage details include an enclosed cabinet with stylish fluted glass door and a box drawer for supplies. A file drawer glides on smooth full-extension ball bearing slides and accommodates letter, legal or A4 sized paperwork. A built-in 4-port USB hub adds convenience as you'll keep all of your devices connected. The unique design of the office desk saves space but provides you with 60 inches to spread out in either direction. Quality construction meets ANSI/BIFMA test standards for safety and performance. Available in Espresso Oak, Harvest Cherry, Heather Gray and White finishes, the beautiful computer desk features Chrome-finished hardware for a simple, elegant and timeless appearance. Add the Cabot Hutch (sold separately) to either side of the L Shaped Desk to create a complete office set. See the full collection for coordinating items available, all backed by the Bush Furniture 1 Year Manufacturer's Warranty.

Available in Espresso Oak, Harvest Cherry, Heather Gray and White finishes, the beautiful computer desk features Chrome-finished hardware for a simple, elegant and timeless appearance. Add the Cabot Hutch (sold separately) to either side of the L Shaped Desk to create a complete office set. See the full collection for coordinating items available, all backed by the Bush Furniture 1 Year Manufacturer's Warranty.

description: This modern take on a classic modality is one of the most popular full-body workouts available. The XTERRA Fitness Air bike Pro offers a tremendous range of workout solutions. The unlimited range of air resistance provides low resistance at slow speeds to high resistance at fast speeds. Simply put, it increases resistance the harder you work, so it's great for everyone. Few other full body workouts are as low impact, easy to use, and burn so many calories in such a small compact design. Whether you are looking to rehab an injury, shake up your WOD (workout of the day), or cross-train for your next race, the XTERRA Fitness AIR650 Airbike Pro has you covered.

features: RESISTANCE: Smooth and unlimited air resistance provides low resistance at slow speeds and high resistance at fast speeds; completely user controlled and great for anything from rehab to high intensity interval training,DRIVE SYSTEM: Industrial grade chain drive system operates as a fixed gear (direct drive) and is extremely durable and reliable,CONSOLE: Performance monitor LCD display is easy to read with all your necessary information - RPM, Speed, Time, Distance, Calories, Watt, Interval Prompt, and Heart Rate,PROGRAMS: Quick mode program buttons include Target Time, Target Distance, Target Calories, Target HR, Interval 20-10, Interval 10-20, and Interval Custom,SEAT: Performance designed seat enables maximum exercise mobility while still providing support and comfort,HANDLEBARS: Ergonomic handlebars are designed with multiple padded grip options and are built to take the most intense upper body workouts,PEDALS: Wide, low profile pedals are anti-skid with dual sided molded pegs for an excellent grip,FOOT PEGS: Large foot pegs are knurled for better grip, allows user to rest their feet during targeted upper-body workouts,ADJUSTABILITY: Seat is fully adjustable (up/down/forward/back) to provide users with a proper fit
name: XTERRA Fitness Air650 Air Upright Cycle Exercise Bike

description: SUMMIT brings innovative value into the kitchen with all-in-one combination units for full-service use. Two electric burners, a refrigerator-freezer, sink, and cabinet space create a utility kitchen with easy-fitting dimensions. The C60ELGLASS is our deluxe combination kitchen in a full 60-in width. At 24-in deep, it leaves you plenty of room to navigate while preparing food on an easy-to-clean smoothtop cooktop with two 120V burners. SUMMIT CT661W, one of our most popular compact refrigerator-freezers, slides in under the counter. This unit uses SUMMIT's exclusive dual evaporator cooling, for energy efficiency with quality results. Automatic defrost eases maintenance in the refrigerator section and a manual defrost zero degree freezer keeps even ice cream frozen. Adjustable glass shelves, door storage, a wine shelf, and a crisper provide added storage options. Two cabinets provide ample space for dry storage. This unit includes a stainless steel work surface with a sink and faucet. Our all-in-one combination kitchens ship fully assembled in two boxes. Just slide the refrigerator in and start serving. Perfect for studio apartments, hotel rooms, dormitories, assisted living facilities, and any other location in need of a full kitchen area at one great price.

description: Versatility is just the beginning with so many Legacy desking options. This 60-inch double pedestal desk is a great choice for professional and home offices alike. It comes with two box-file pedestals that each have one box drawer and one file drawer that accepts both letter and legal filing. All drawers lock and include ergonomically designed drawer pulls for convenience and ease in operation. Adjustable glides on the bottom of the base keep the desktop level and are easy to adjust. Two wire management grommets keep cables clear of work areas. Finished in an stylish Ash Grey laminate, this desk coordinates with other Legacy furniture. The Legacy collection is constructed of a 1-inch thick thermal fused melamine laminate with a 3-millimeter commercial grade matching PVC edge. Laminates are scratch, stain and scald resistant. Legacy casegoods are backed by a 10-year limited manufacturer's warranty.

description: Enjoy all the benefits of a rehabilitative session from home. Among its many benefits, whole body vibrations (WBV) have shown to calm the nervous system and relieve stress and pain throughout your body. Therapeutic vibrations increase blood flow, improving your circulation , protecting your nerves and bones, repairing old injuries, and loosening stiff joints — providing you with true, lasting pain relief and a greater range of motion as you continue to improve. With a robust 200W motor, our mini waver packs the same punch as its full-sized counterpart - the bestselling life pro waver vibration machine. Take this vibrating platform with you on road trips to upkeep your fitness on the go. Plus, thanks to its compact size, it’s easy to find a place to store it when not in use. description: The ERG700 Rower provides an unparalleled full-body workout. The full body rhythmic nature of rowing makes it wonderfully efficient at burning calories while also developing flexibility and strength. Rowing is impact-free and the intensity is completely user-controlled.   The large 5.5in bright blue backlit console with height and angle adjustment includes motivating programs to keep you involved, inspired, and reaching your goals. Performance is top-of-the-class with a smooth action aluminum rail system, convenient fold up design, industrial strength handle strap, flex pedals with easy adjustment, and the combination of both air and magnetic resistance (16 levels) for an exercise experience second to none. The XTERRA performance monitor clearly displays time, distance, strokes/min, count, calories, heart rate, watts, level and a program graphic of resistance over time. It also features 10 effective workout programs for a wide variety of workouts. When you're done, the rower easily moves with the help of built-in transportation wheels and folds for storage to take up less floor space.

description: Bring home two pieces of fitness equipment in one.  Work up a sweat and add variety to your workouts with the 2-in-1 Cardio Dual Trainer, which can be used as an elliptical machine or an exercise bike.  It offers magnetic resistance and features patented elliptical motion design technology; the pass-through frame promises comfort, while the 2-way adjustable seat makes it ideal for any user. The programmable electronic exercise console easily displays your workout metrics. The 2-in-1 Cardio Dual Trainer let you maximize your workout sessions in the comfort of your home.

description: There are 7 days in a week and the fēnix 7 Multisport GPS Watch is built to go strong for all of them. This silver watch with a graphite band is made to meet any athletic or outdoor challenge with cutting-edge training features, sports apps, 24/7 health and wellness monitoring, and more. Use trusted button controls or a new touchscreen interface to access selections. Gain performance insights and metrics that help you manage your exertion and build stamina. Optimize recovery and overall wellness by monitoring heart rate, respiration, stress, sleep, and more (this device is intended to give an estimation of your activity and metrics; it is not a medical device). GPS and outdoor navigation sensors guide your outings off the beaten path. To complement your tamer days, connected features include smart notifications (when connected to a compatible smartphone), music storage, and Garmin Pay contactless payments in supported countries and payment networks.

features: Rugged, sophisticated multisport GPS watch featuring always-on 1.3-in display, long battery life, and new ultra-tough athletic design with fiber-reinforced polymer case,Trusted button controls that work-inany environment are matched with a highly responsive touchscreen-inerface for quick, convenient access to selections,Takes training to the next level with endurance and real-time stamina tracking, training status, advanced performance metrics, and 30+ built-in sports apps,24/7 health and wellness monitoring with wrist-based heart rate, Pulse Ox (not available in all countries), stress and enhanced sleep tracking (this device is intended to give an estimation of activity and metrics; it is not a medical device),Navigates the outdoors with built-in sensors for 3-axis compass, gyroscope, and barometric altimeter; supports multi-GNSS satellite systems (GPS, GLONASS, and Galileo),Preloaded maps for thousands of golf courses and ski resorts worldwide; download TopoActive maps for any region to keep explorations on track,Access to smart notifications (when paired with a compatible smartphone), music storage and our Garmin Pay contactless payments in supported countries and payment networks,Battery performance: up to 18 days in smartwatch mode, up to 57 hours in GPS mode and up to 40 days in Expedition mode,Silver with graphite band

description: The PRO3900 two-piece set Olympic Weight Bench is designed for versatility for your stress-free out of your exercise routines. This unique set is an ideal choice for any level user looking to building, toning, and maintaining muscle mass. Features of this home exercise equipment include includes 1 Olympic Weight Bench,  and 1 Squat Rack.   The bench is equipped with high-density padding with 5-position settings backrest and 2-position setting seat cushion. The bench also equipped with an easy-lift lever and 2 built-in transport wheels to make moving and storing the bench an effortless experience.   The stand-alone squat rack is built on robust 60x60 powder-coated square tubing with the Double-deck Safety and 2 sets of integrated catches. The rack also designed with no-pinch catch design to provides extra safety and prevent injury to hands and grip during racking and un-racking.  The weight bench is designed to support a maximum user weight of 300 pounds and maximum weight set of 300 pounds.

description: CityPost 42in tall cable railing kits can be ordered to fit your needs regardless of your project layout. All kits come with enough posts to install at a maximum center-to-center spacing of 6FT (example: 24FT kit includes 5 posts). All you need to do is measure each deck/stair side and order a kit that most closely match in length (always round up to the nearest size to ensure proper fit as kits can be trimmed down to your exact length).  All kits come with posts that are pre-drilled, mounting bolts, CityPost patented top rail bracket, all cable and cable hardware is marine grade 316 stainless steel (10 percent extra cable is included with every order). In addition, all kits come with metal top rail that is powder coated to match the posts. 100 percent of components are included to complete your railing. [Example] For a deck with three sides that measure [12FT, 24FT,12FT] you will want to order three CityPost kits: (2) 12FT kits and (1) 24FT kit. For any corners/changes in direction simply add CityPost top rail sleeves to your order to conceal any top rail corner joints. For LOWES ordering questions, please reach out to CityPost at 855-get-city to speak to an ordering expert.  We will be happy to walk you through the process. Note, swaging tool and cable cutter not included. Not recommended withing 3 miles of salt water (order stainless steel post option in that case).

description: The advanced XTERRA SB250 Recumbent Bike with sleek lines and premium features provide a smooth lower-body workout, walk-thru solid frame design, and advanced console features.  The compact design maximizes your use of space with a small footprint while providing a workout that is low impact and effective.  And with a smooth belt drive system, friction-free magnetic resistance, and easy adjust lever seat slide, the SB250 Recumbent Bike delivers a quiet and effective workout. The advanced console features a large 5.5in easy to read blue backlit LCD screen that displays everything from speed and distance to calories and heart rate.  The 12 pre-set, 4 custom user, 1 body-fat, 1 watt, and 5 heart rate programs with 24 levels of resistance are sure to challenge users of all fitness levels. The long list of features is matched only by the passion of those looking to get serious about their workouts.  Start on the road to fitness today with the new XTERRA SB250 Recumbent Bike and exceed your expectations.

description:
SUMMIT brings innovative value into the kitchen with all-in-one combination units for full-service use. Two electric burners, a refrigerator-freezer, sink, and cabinet space create a utility kitchen with easy-fitting dimensions.

The C48EL is our deluxe combination kitchen in a full 48" width. At 24" deep, it leaves you plenty of room to navigate while preparing food on two 120V coil burners.

SUMMIT CT661W, one of our most popular compact refrigerator-freezers, slides in under the counter. This unit uses SUMMIT's exclusive dual evaporator cooling, for energy efficiency with quality results. Automatic defrost eases maintenance in the refrigerator section and a manual defrost zero degree freezer keeps even ice cream frozen. Adjustable glass shelves, door storage, a wine shelf, and a crisper provide added storage options.

A side cabinet provides ample space for dry storage. This unit includes a stainless steel work surface with a sink and faucet.

Our all-in-one combination kitchens ship fully assembled in two boxes. Just slide the refrigerator in and start serving. Perfect for studio apartments, hotel rooms, dormitories, assisted living facilities, and any other location in need of a full kitchen area at one great price.

description: Kick off overwhelming emotions, rejuvenate your whole body! Healthy living means not more feeling of sluggish, achy, and depressive. This luxury comfort full body massage mat is built for whole body rejuvenating; utilizing the do-it-all concept or spot-focus physiotherapy from head to calf with its shiatsu and vibration massage to maximize comfort, relax and relieve weary body from overwhelming emotions, sensations, and depression. Shiatsu head massage is built into the raised up comfortable pillow; offering three selective intensities and two massage directions. Ten vibration motors located in four different reflex zones to create powerful vibration massage to melt away stress and soothe tense muscles all over the body. Four vibration massage zones can be activated together or individually and they are professionally designed according to the human vertebral physiological curve; you can customize massage on shoulder, back, lumbar, and legs one by one or simultaneously. The removable, inflatable waist support cushion maximizes your relaxation while lying down on the mat. Its intelligent handheld controller with LED indicator light lets you customize massaging zones when you are leaning back and relaxing. Three selective preset working timers; home use AC adapter included.

description: Portable and Convenient Utility Cart Use this portable utility cart anywhere you need storage solutions—whether it be in your garage, bathroom, bedroom, home office, or office. Four drawers and two open shelves offer you plenty of storage space so you can organize your items neatly. The drawers work well for items like pens, staplers, or other desk supplies, while you can store bigger items, such as file boxes and larger items on the spacious shelves. In addition, you can place items on top for display or storage.   Easily roll and move this cart from place to place as needs change. You can bring supplies where you need them without carrying large drawers, containers, or boxes. Each wheel has 360-degree casters, which allow you to turn the cart in any direction.  Designed for everyday use, this cart has a strong, durable metal frame, and each of the plastic drawers is mold- and mildew-resistant. At just 9.24 lbs. (4.19 kg), the cart is easy to maneuver even when loaded with supplies.

description: You can easily achieve the fitness effects of walking, jogging and running with the convenient speed adjustment knob. The clear LED touch display monitors your movement data in real time. description: The XTERRA SB150 Recumbent Bike provides a smooth lower-body workout, walk-thru solid frame design, and advanced console features.  The compact design maximizes your use of space with a small footprint while providing a workout that is low impact and effective.  And with a smooth belt drive system, friction-free magnetic resistance, and easy adjust seat slide, the SB150 Recumbent Bike delivers a quiet and effective workout. The advanced console features a large 3.7in easy to read blue backlit LCD screen that displays everything from speed and distance to calories and heart rate.  The 12 pre-set, 4 custom user, 1 body-fat, and 5 heart rate programs with 24 levels of resistance are sure to challenge users of all fitness levels.
descriptionHtml: The XTERRA SB150 Recumbent Bike provides a smooth lower-body workout, walk-thru solid frame design, and advanced console features. The compact design maximizes your use of space with a small footprint while providing a workout that is low impact and effective. And with a smooth belt drive system, friction-free magnetic resistance, and easy adjust seat slide, the SB150 Recumbent Bike delivers a quiet and effective workout. The advanced console features a large 3.7in easy to read blue backlit LCD screen that displays everything from speed and distance to calories and heart rate. The 12 pre-set, 4 custom user, 1 body-fat, and 5 heart rate programs with 24 levels of resistance are sure to challenge users of all fitness levels.

description: Versatility is just the beginning with so many Legacy desking options. This classic corner workstation has a curved center for a seamless transition between desk and return. On this Right Corner Credenza, the return attaches to the right hand side and it is not reversible. It comes with one box-file pedestal that has one box drawer and one file drawer that accepts both letter and legal filing. Both drawers lock and include ergonomically designed drawer pulls for convenience and ease in operation. Adjustable glides on the bottom of the base keep the desktop level and are easy to adjust. Wire management grommets keep cables clear of work areas. Finished in an stylish Ash Grey laminate, this desk coordinates with other Legacy furniture. The Legacy collection is constructed of a 1-inch thick thermal fused melamine laminate with a 3-millimeter commercial grade matching PVC edge. Laminates are scratch, stain and scald resistant. Legacy casegoods are backed by a 10-year limited manufacturer's warranty.

description: The full body rhythmic nature of rowing makes it wonderfully efficient at burning calories while also developing flexibility and strength. Plus, the zen-like water movement you hear from the ERG600W multi-bladed impeller can be soothing and meditative. Large and easy to read 5.5in LCD console with height and angle adjustment includes motivating programmable modes to keep you involved, inspired, and reaching your goals. Performance is top-of-the-class with a smooth action dual aluminum rail system, industrial strength handle strap, flex pedals with easy numbered adjustments, and durable XTERRA multi-bladed impeller for a water rowing experience second to none. When you are not using your ERG600W Rower, simply wheel it out of the way and stand it up for storage. Start making waves with your workouts today on the XTERRA Fitness ERG600W Rower.

You can use it to exercise the arms, abdomen, legs, buttocks and other parts to help you have a perfect body. description: Run at a higher level with the Slate Gray Forerunner 255 Running Smartwatch from Garmin. These running smartwatches help you train and recover smarter with training status, running power, multi-band GPS and daily suggested workouts that adapt to your performance and goals. Plus, other new features, such as race widget help you plan your race-day strategy, and morning report with HRV status reveals your overall health alongside the day ahead. And with Garmin Pay contactless payments with a supported card, it’s never been easier to buy that post-workout coffee. It has more than 30 activity profiles, including triathlon, cycling, swimming, and more. With Forerunner 255, you can get a continuous picture of your health, from training and recovery to sleep quality and overall wellness. It has up to 14 days of battery life in smartwatch mode and up to 30 hours in GPS mode.

description: CityPost 36in tall cable railing kits can be ordered to fit your needs regardless of your project layout. All kits come with enough posts to install at a maximum center-to-center spacing of 6FT (example: 24FT kit includes 5 posts). All you need to do is measure each deck/stair side and order a kit that most closely match in length (always round up to the nearest size to ensure proper fit as kits can be trimmed down to your exact length).  All kits come with posts that are pre-drilled, mounting bolts, CityPost patented top rail bracket, all cable and cable hardware is marine grade 316 stainless steel (10 percent extra cable is included with every order). In addition, all kits come with metal top rail that is powder coated to match the posts. 100 percent of components are included to complete your railing. [Example] For a deck with three sides that measure [12FT, 24FT,12FT] you will want to order three CityPost kits: (2) 12FT kits and (1) 24FT kit. For any corners/changes in direction simply add CityPost top rail sleeves to your order to conceal any top rail corner joints. For LOWES ordering questions, please reach out to CityPost at 855-get-city to speak to an ordering expert.  We will be happy to walk you through the process. Note, swaging tool and cable cutter not included. Not recommended withing 3 miles of salt water (order stainless steel post option in that case).

description: For 18 years, Post Protector has provided simple, slide-on barrier protection for in-ground posts. It works in conjunction with the chemical preservative as an important additional layer of protection against soil-dwelling and atmospheric decay fungi and insect infestation. It’s first important to understand decay. Many believe that moisture causes decay; moisture is not the cause of decay but is one of three conditions needed for decay to occur, those conditions being moisture, oxygen, and a suitable temperature. These conditions enable the soil-dwelling or atmospheric decay fungi, as well as termites and other subterranean insects, to feed on the wood fiber. So the decay/degradation of ground-contact wood is not caused by moisture but by the action of wood destroying organisms feeding on the wood. The chemical preservatives protection strategy is to poison the wood fiber, rendering it an unsuitable food source for the wood destroying organisms. The downside to that approach is that all chemical preservatives eventually lose resistance to decay and insect infestation. Post Protector becomes the perfect complement to the pressure treated (or cedar) post by simply providing a physical barrier isolating the post so the wood-destroying organisms have no access to the post altogether.

Meet any athletic or outdoor challenge with cutting-edge training features, sports apps, and health monitoring. Styled for smaller-sized wrists, the watch’s fresh new design adds a new touchscreen interface to access selections along with the watch’s trusted button controls. Gain performance insights and metrics that help you manage your exertion and build stamina. Optimize recovery with 24/7 health and wellness monitoring of heart rate, respiration, stress, sleep, and more (this device is intended to give an estimation of your activity and metrics; it is not a medical device). descriptionHtml: There are 7 days in a week, and the smaller-sized Silver fēnix 7S Multisport GPS Smartwatch with Graphite Band is built to go strong for all of them. Meet any athletic or outdoor challenge with cutting-edge training features, sports apps, and health monitoring. Styled for smaller-sized wrists, the watch’s fresh new design adds a new touchscreen interface to access selections along with the watch’s trusted button controls. Gain performance insights and metrics that help you manage your exertion and build stamina. Optimize recovery with 24/7 health and wellness monitoring of heart rate, respiration, stress, sleep, and more (this device is intended to give an estimation of your activity and metrics; it is not a medical device). GPS and outdoor navigation sensors guide your outings off the beaten path. And to complement your tamer days, connected features include smart notifications (when connected to a compatible smartphone), music storage, and Garmin Pay contactless payments in supported countries and payment networks.
features: Smaller-sized multisport GPS watch features always-on 1.2-in display, long battery life, and ultra-tough athletic design with fiber-reinforced polymer case,Trusted button controls work-inany environment; highly responsive touchscreen-inerface for quick, convenient access to selections,Endurance and real-time stamina tracking, training status, advanced performance metrics, and 30+ built-in sports apps,24/7 health and wellness monitoring with wrist-based heart rate, Pulse Ox (not available in all countries), stress, and enhanced sleep tracking (this device is intended to give an estimation of activity and metrics; it is not a medical device),Navigates the outdoors with built-in sensors for 3-axis compass, gyroscope and barometric altimeter; supports multi-GNSS satellite systems (GPS, GLONASS and Galileo),Preloaded maps for thousands of golf courses and ski resorts worldwide; download TopoActive maps for any region to keep your explorations on track,Access to smart notifications when paired with compatible smartphone, music storage, and Garmin Pay contactless payment solution in supported countries and payment networks,Battery performance: up to 11 days in smartwatch mode, up to 37 hours in GPS mode and up to 26 days in Expedition mode,Includes charging/data cable and documentation
name: Garmin fēnix 7S Multisport GPS Smartwatch (Silver, Graphite Band)

description: The Cary six drawer rolling cart is a versatile storage solution for office, kitchen, bedroom or anywhere where organization is needed. Solidly constructed from pine wood and finished in a handsome black. Six equal size drawers and an ample top can go next to a desk or craft table to put items within reach. Extra wide to hold more of what you need tucked away. Soft contoured handle cut out is easy on the touch and creates a clean, modern look. Drawers can be easily removed and used as a tray to transport your items to your workspace. Casters make this piece mobile to go into any room easily.

description: IDeal's iMobile MSC-6KLP 6,000 lb. is a ‘low profile’ mobile single column lift perfect for limited space and situations where lift portability is important. The low profile design and drive-over ramps make ‘drive-over’ vehicle loading possible, while the pallet jack feature also allows the lift to be positioned under the vehicle for loading. Due to the unique design and portability feature, the MSC-6KLP is the perfect solution for a homeowner with limited space or a shop looking to improve work flow or gain additional revenue from previously unusable space.

description: Owning your own in-home gym does not have to be large, bulky nor heavy any! The sunny health and fitness walk station slim treadmill is versatile, subtle and flexible; place the treadmill anywhere in your home and jump on for a quick stroll. Get your heart rate going while getting some work done, watching your favorite videos or even reading a book. Simply place the treadmill under your desk, use the included remote control to adjust the speed and get active! The sunny health and fitness walk station slim treadmill is stylish, versatile, practical and very convenient - all you have to do is just hop on!

description: At GE Appliances, we bring good things to life. Our goal is to help people improve their lives at home by providing quality appliances that were made for real life. Whether it's enjoying the tradition of making meals from scratch or tackling a mountain of muddy jeans and soccer jerseys, GE Appliances are crafted to support any and every task in the home.
descriptionHtml: At GE Appliances, we bring good things to life. Our goal is to help people improve their lives at home by providing quality appliances that were made for real life. Whether it's enjoying the tradition of making meals from scratch or tackling a mountain of muddy jeans and soccer jerseys, GE Appliances are crafted to support any and every task in the home.
features: Fingerprint Resistant Stainless - easily wipe away smudges and fingerprints for a look that's always sparkling clean,LED Lighting - quickly find even the smallest items thanks to flush-mounted LED lighting, which sheds crisp, even light throughout the interior,Edge-to-Edge Shelves - store more of your favorite items and enjoy organizational flexibility on every level with glass shelves that extend from wall to wall,Clear Door Shelves - adjustable, see-through door shelves provide flexible storage options for even large containers, and free up valuable space inside the refrigerator,Interior Storage Drawers - two refrigerator pull out drawers with clear fronts provide the perfect, sealed environment to keep your produce organized,External Dispenser - easily access clean water and filtered ice from a dispenser conveniently located on the outside of the door,Easy Access Icemaker - automatically create cubed or crushed ice thanks to a factory-installed, low profile icemaker,Advanced Water Filtration - reduces impurities, lead and trace pharmaceuticals from water and ice (Removes 98% of ibuprofen, atenolol, fluoxetine, progesterone and trimethoprim; impurities are not necessarily in all users’ water),Electronic Display - forget the guesswork in setting the refrigerator temperature with an electronic display that allows for precise settings
name: GE 25.3-cu ft Side-by-Side Refrigerator with Ice Maker (Stainless Steel)

description: Glide confidently and comfortably on the NordicTrack AirGlide 14i Elliptical. The soft hand grips, cushioned pedals and included workout fan are just what you need on those long workout sessions. To keep you pushing forward to reach your fitness goals, the elliptical comes with a 30-day free trial of iFIT - where you can access 1,000s of different workout videos. The videos are led by top-rated trainers and take place in interesting locations all over the world, from tropical islands to city streets. As you exercise, you'll be able to track your stats as well as play your favorite songs from the Bluetooth-enabled speakers. 300-pound max user capacity.

description: A utility trailer can be incredibly useful for a wide range of tasks. Whether you're moving furniture, transporting landscaping materials, hauling equipment for a home improvement project, or simply running errands, a utility trailer can provide the extra space you need to get the job done efficiently. These trailers are easy to maneuver, lightweight, and can be attached to a variety of vehicles, making them a versatile addition to any home or business. With the ability to carry up to several hundred pounds, a small utility trailer can save you time and effort, while also protecting your vehicle from damage caused by overloading.

description: The XTERRA Fitness TR200 treadmill combines the quality and performance you desire with the flexibility of a machine that can be easily folded up and stored away when not in use. The heart pounding speed range up to 10 mph is powered by a smooth and quiet 2.25 HP motor. The 12 preset programs offer unmatched variety while the 3 manual incline settings allow you to push your limits.   XTRASOFT Cushioned Deck technology and a large 16 x 50in running surface keep you comfortable so you can workout longer. To help keep you in your training zone, hand grip pulse sensors are conveniently mounted on the side handlebars. They monitor your heart rate without having to take your hands off the handlebars.  The large 5.2in blue backlit LCD provides you with all your important workout feedback while the intuitive button layout incorporates direct access speed buttons to quickly access your favorite speeds. Great for interval training. The integrated book rack and accessory holders keep your reading material, remote control, and anything else you want close by.   When your workout is complete a folding deck design with built in transport wheels is easy to use and allows for storage when not in use. Simply fold and store your treadmill out of the way.

description: Rowing is the perfect low-impact workout to help you burn fat, build strength, and improve cardiovascular health by engaging all major muscle groups. With 8 levels of magnetic resistance you can challenge yourself every time you use the machine. The solid steel frame construction of the ERG220 rower with full-length dual aluminum rails offers a smooth, quiet, and effective exercise experience. Comfort and convenience are at the core of the XTERRA Fitness ERG220 magnetic rower. Padded handlebars and a comfort molded seat ensure that you keep going back for more. The elevated seat makes it easier for you to get on and off with ease. When you have reached the end of your workout, the rower folds and stores easily with the help of built-in transportation wheels.

description: The Schwinn IC4 Bike provides a premium, heart-pumping indoor cycling experience and features an intuitive resistance knob with 100 levels of magnetic resistance, a beautiful backlit LCD display, and easy-reach cradles for 3 lb. dumbbells. Digitally immerse yourself in a world of virtual races, exotic locales, and stunning trails from around the globe with connectivity to popular cycling apps like JRNY, Peloton, Explore the World, Zwift, and more. Personalize your IC4 experience with adaptive workouts, real-time coaching, virtual destinations, and on-demand classes. Keep working out with JNRY wherever you go from your phone or tablet; try the Mobile-Only Membership free for 2 months. With the IC4, you’ll escape the everyday and stay on track for a life well-lived.  *JRNY® subscription auto renews annually at then-current annual rates, plus applicable taxes, unless canceled at least 48 hours before free period ends.

description: DEWALT DW22838 10 piece 3/8-in drive socket set includes the eight most common size sockets and two 1/4-in adapters. The pivoting organization pins allow for customized application based storage, and the space inside the case allows for storage of a common 10-in hand wrench (Not included). These sockets are made of high impact resistant material to give overall durability to the case, and have recessed corners that distribute torque across flats, promoting life of the socket. These sockets have a small foot print and are easy to carry. The sockets feature large laser etched markings that make each socket easily identifiable, and are thinner than pneumatic wrench sockets for tough to access areas.

Keep your food fresh and reduce freezer burn with our variable speed compressor (EvenTemp Cooling System) that reacts quickly to temperature fluctuations and constantly circulates cold air throughout the fresh food and freezer compartments. description: The CRAFTSMAN Matte Black Aluminum Truck Tool Box fits most mid-sized trucks and is designed with a low profile, giving you ample storage space and allows for greater visibility through your truck’s rear window. With the one-touch push buttons, you can lock and unlock from either side for easy access. The auto-lift gas springs make opening and closing the box easy and smooth, opening 90 degrees giving you room to load and unload your cargo. Provides extra security and protection of your valuables and helps prevents break-ins with the fully welded loop strikers and locking paddle handle. Keep your cargo and equipment dry from the elements with the weather-block rubber seal. The removable plastic sliding tray has dividers so you can keep your smaller tools organized and accessible.

description: The CRAFTSMAN Aluminum Crossover Truck Tool Box is engineered with fully welded aluminum construction to ensure lasting durability and features a sleek matte black finish. Its slim, space-saving design gives you more truck bed room to store other items. The one-touch access push button locks on both sides and automatically opens with the smooth-opening gas springs. The weather-block rubber seal keeps your stored items protected from the elements, so they are dry and ready to use. It is keyed with a locking paddle handle that latches to provide extra security and protection of your stored loose items. Includes a drill-free mounting kit and a removable sliding tool tray that keeps your tools organized, accessible, and ready for any job. Fits most full-sized pickups (see product images for compatibility).

description: This 4.8 cu. ft. capacity top load washer from Maytag delivers the stain-fighting power that’s built to handle tough loads. Use Extra Power for boosted stain fighting on any wash cycle while the Power™ impeller helps dissolve soils with a vigorous wash motion. description: Forget pulling still-damp loads from the dryer—With Sensor Dry, the dryer can detect moisture and automatically adjust drying time for loads of all sizes—saving energy with less wear and tear on clothes. You can even save time with ultra large capacity that fits more clothes in every load. Plus, keep your dryer clean, efficient and safe with the FlowSense™ Duct Clogging Indicator – that lets you know when your ducts need cleaning to avoid lint buildup, improves the dryer’s performance for greater efficiency and lower utility bills and gives you safer, worry-free operation with fewer service calls.

Plus, keep your dryer clean, efficient and safe with the FlowSense™ Duct Clogging Indicator – that lets you know when your ducts need cleaning to avoid lint buildup, improves the dryer’s performance for greater efficiency and lower utility bills and gives you safer, worry-free operation with fewer service calls.

description: There are 7 days in a week. And the fēnix 7X Sapphire Solar Multisport GPS Watch is built to go strong for all of them. It features Black DLC Titanium and a Black Band, and has a big 1.4 in. display, built-in LED flashlight, and Power Sapphire solar charging lens. It has the long-lasting battery life to sustain your athletic and outdoor challenges. Use trusted button controls or the new touchscreen interface to access selections. Gain performance insights and metrics that help you manage your exertion and build stamina. Optimize recovery with 24/7 health and wellness monitoring of heart rate, respiration, stress, sleep, and more (this device is intended to give an estimation of your activity and metrics; it is not a medical device). Outdoor navigation sensors and new multi-band GNSS technology help guide you with a higher level of positioning accuracy, even in challenging environments. Plus, you’ll have preloaded TopoActive maps and worldwide ski and golf maps right on your wrist. To complement your tamer days, connected features include smart notifications when connected to a compatible smartphone, music storage, and Garmin Pay contactless payments in supported countries and payment networks.

features: Long-running solar powered multisport GPS watch with scratch-resistant Power Sapphire lens,Trusted button controls that work-inany environment are matched with a highly responsive touchscreen-inerface for quick, convenient access to selections,Always-on 1.4-in display uses the sun’s energy to extend battery life,Takes training to the next level with endurance and real-time stamina tracking, training status, advanced performance metrics, and 30+ built-in sports apps,24/7 health and wellness monitoring with wrist-based heart rate, Pulse Ox (not available in all countries), stress, and enhanced sleep tracking,Navigates the outdoors with a higher level of positioning accuracy, with multi-band frequency and GNSS network support (GPS, GLONASS and Galileo) plus built-in sensors for 3-axis compass, gyroscope, and barometric altimeter,Preloaded TopoActive maps, and maps for thousands of golf courses and ski resorts worldwide,Built-in Wi-Fi connectivity lets user download maps for any continent at any time without using a computer,Built-in LED flashlight

description: The XTERRA Fitness ERG160 Rower has everything you need to help you achieve your fitness goals in the comfort of your home. The magnetic flywheel resistance is smooth, quiet, and easily adjustable between 8 different levels to adapt to the demands of your training level. The durable aluminum slide rail on the ERG160 ensures a smooth rowing experience pull after pull.    Stay on top of your most important workout data with the easy-to-read high-contrast LED display. The console also features a built-in accessory tray so you can make use of your favorite fitness apps, your favorite book, or simply keep your phone right where you can see it.   Comfort and convenience are at the core of the XTERRA Fitness ERG160 magnetic rower with a foam padded handlebar, and a molded foam seat. Large, easily adjustable foot straps keep you secure, so you can feel confident and in control while you push your limits. A built-in water bottle holder is right at your feet, so you can stay hydrated, or keep your keys and other personal belongings within reach when you need them most.

description: Sweat with Small Things…Sure you want be physically fit and healthy, but finding time for a thoroughly effective cardiovascular workout is just plain difficult with your schedule. Besides, you can always get back in shape once you have enough space for a full-size elliptical machine or treadmill. Sound familiar? It’s time to leave excuses behind along with any oversized clothing those excuses have earned you. The Stamina® InMotion® E1000 Compact Strider eliminates any •reason• to procrastinate about the health of your body and mind. The incredibly compact, portable, and affordable elliptical lets you conveniently work up a healthy sweat nearly anywhere, anytime.……Efficient Cardio Results…Ever wonder why elliptical machines are so often occupied at the gym? Elliptical trainer workouts are proven to burn a similar number of calories as jogging does, efficiently increasing stamina and energy while toning your hips, buttocks, thighs, and legs. Unlike jogging, however, ellipticals help you reach your fitness and weight loss goals through a low-impact routine that won’t jar your back, knees, hips, or ankles. The Stamina® InMotion® E1000 Compact Strider offers the all results without the endless membership fees, crowds, and hassle of driving to the gym.……Always-Available Cardio Workout…The Stamina® InMotion® E1000 Compact Strider is designed for easy portability and complete convenience. description: Every DIYer or tradesman needs a reliable set of sockets for driving nuts and bolts. Complete your toolkit with this 16-piece SAE 3/4-inch drive 12-point shallow socket set from CRAFTSMAN. The set comes with a 72-tooth ratchet so you’re all set to complete your projects. This broad assortment of sockets can be used for almost any household project or professional job. Whether you’re repairing a car, installing steel trusses, or doing DIY repairs, you’ll find the right size socket for every task in this set. These standard sockets will work well with any 3/4-in ratchet, extension, torque wrench, or breaker bar. Each piece is made with a corrosion-resistant coating for long life and visible size markings for ease of use. The 12 points in each socket means you’ll get more torque and less spin without stripping the bolt’s head. Get this versatile SAE 3/4-in drive 12-point shallow socket 16-piece set  at Lowes.com.

description: Run, walk, or dash to your fitness goals with the sunny health and fitness SF-T7917 performance treadmill. Exercise comfortably on the spacious (19in x 52 in) treadmill deck with built-in shock absorption technology that eases impact on leg joints as you exercise on the in-home treadmill. Designed for vigorous and long-lasting workouts, this incline treadmill supports up to 265LBS. powered by a 2.0-peak horsepower motor, the wide treadmill operates between 0.6mph and 10mph. Increase workout intensity on the fly with 15 levels of automatic incline. Make quick adjustments to your speed and incline with the convenient handrail controls and the quick buttons on the console. View your heart rate quickly on the cardiovascular machine when you grab the hand pulse grips. Track your time, distance, speed, pulse, incline, and calories-burned on the built-in performance monitor. Want to mix up your workout? Take advantage of 15 pre-installed workouts that automatically adjust speed and incline.

description: Save space and get a killer workout with this effective, compact, and easy-to-use trio trainer workout machine. It combines three of the best cardioid tools you find at a gym: an elliptical, upright bike, and recumbent bike. Its magnetic resistance can be adjusted with the simple turn of a knob, so it’s easy to get the workout you need. Comfortable and convenient, this machine has 8 preset workout levels, built-in heart-rate hand pulse sensors, and a media shelf for your phone, tablet, or book/magazine. Easily adjust the seat and backrest cushion vertically and horizontally with a pass-through frame design for comfort. Each of the exercises possible with this unique machine is low-impact, making it perfect for people with painful joints. This makes it easy to get a multifaceted cardioid workout effortlessly. Whether you prefer to work out in the garage or from the comfort of your bedroom, this machine doesn't take up much space. It measures 42" x 19" x 63". For the upright stationary bike, we included U-shaped handlebars, which are fixed in front and have a built-in hand-grip heart-rate monitor system. For the elliptical part of this trio trainer, we have included traditional dual-action independent handlebars. Finally, the recumbent bike handlebars wrap around the base of the reclined seat for a more relaxed and comfortable position, and the reclined backrest cushion allows for longer periods of fitness training time.

description: From a slow stroll to a power walk, The XTERRA Fitness WS200 WalkSlim Treadmill™ keeps you moving . The smart design features a bright, multi-window white LED display, Bluetooth with FTMS to connect to 3rd party apps like Kinomap and Zwift. Plus, the unit arrives 100% assembled, with no tools required.  Simply remove from the box, and you will be on your way to fitness!  Other convenient features include direct access speed buttons for quick workout changes, hand grip pulse sensors, USB charger port, and foldable handles.  The powerful XTERRA 2.5 HP motor provides speeds up to 8 mph. The large 16” x 50” belt with XTRASoft™ Deck Cushioning, keeps you comfortable without breaking your stride. When your workout is complete, easily fold up the treadmill and roll away with the built-in transport wheels. The low storage profile keeps your space clear when not in use. The XTERRA Fitness WS200 WalkSlim Treadmill™ keeps you moving without breaking the bank.

description: This electric walking treadmill is a perfect way for you to work out and relax. This electric walking treadmill can help you improve your cardiovascular health, burn fat, and regulate lower body muscles. Therefore, whether you want to exercise or get your body into the desired shape, this electric walking treadmill is an ideal choice. It is equipped with an LED display, so you can monitor the time, speed, distance, and calories burned. Moreover, the 6.5 inch thickness of the treadmill will help you save space, while the widened running belt will satisfy all your fitness needs. Also, the light-weight design and two flexible wheels allow you to easily move it to any desired location. For those of you who don't have the time to go to the gym, this treadmill is a perfect choice.

description: The YUTRAX® HC1500 High-Capacity Trailer is built to work. Featuring a heavy-duty all- welded construction with rugged steel mesh, this trailer can withstand abuse day-in and day-out. Perfect for homesteading, the massive bed of the HC1500 can haul as much as 22 cubic feet of material and loads as heavy as 1,500 lbs. Use it for hauling firewood or mulch around the yard, feed and seed around the farm or fencing materials across the ranch. Hunters can use the trailer to haul gear out for early season treestand sets or game retrieval during the hunting season making the HC1500 a true, year-round product. The removable side rails and tailgate make for easy loading and unloading of all materials. The HC1500 features large off-road flotation tires that make for a smoother ride while the sealed ball bearings require no maintenance. The powder coated finish resists rust and corrosion. Easily haul your HC1500 with the pin style hitch design with the pin included. Trust the YUTRAX® HC1500 High-Capacity Trailer for all of your toughest jobs, big or small.

description: The CRAFTSMAN Portable Power Station and 1200 Peak Amp Jump Starter (CMXCESM256) gives users a feature-rich experience, whether they are jump starting their car or using the device as a portable power supply. The unit's powerful internal AGM battery allows you to power a range of devices including smartphones, tablets, power tools, and much more. In addition, the CMXCESM256 features several outlet types, allowing you to operate or charge a wide variety of devices. The unit features a 12V 6A DC output port, a 110V AC household outlet with a 200-watt inverter, and a four-port USB hub. The USB hub includes two type C 3A USB ports and two type A 2.4A USB ports, which are optimized for Apple and Android devices. The jump starter delivers 1200 peak amps of power, enough to start 4- to 8-cylinder engines, and also features a reverse hook-up alarm to prevent damage to the battery if the clamps are accidentally reversed. In addition to functioning as a power station and a jump starter, the CRAFTSMAN CMXCESM256 includes a 100-PSI automatic air compressor and a built-in LED area light. Additional features include a digital display and color-coded, 4-gauge, 24-inch booster cables with heavy-duty metal clamps for secure connections.

Additional features include a digital display and color-coded, 4-gauge, 24-inch booster cables with heavy-duty metal clamps for secure connections.

description: The 7-Piece Flip Impact Socket Set includes ten sizes combined into five sockets and two nested adapters. The two nested adapters allow for dual drive (1/4-Inch, 1/2-Inch) capability. The sockets are designed for use with an impact driver including Klein's Impact Wrench (Cat. Nos. BAT20CW, BAT20CW1) and Impact Driver (Cat. Nos. BAT20CD, BAT20CD1). Easy-to-use flip feature allows for quick changes between sizes and reduces the number of tools in the tool bag. All sockets and adapters store in a convenient case for easy portability.
