description: There are 7 days in a week and the fēnix 7 Sapphire Solar Multisport GPS Watch is built to go strong for all of them. It features Black DLC Titanium and a Black Band. With a 1.3 in. display and scratch-resistant Power Sapphire solar charging lens, it has the battery life to sustain your athletic and outdoor challenges. Use trusted button controls or the new touchscreen interface to access selections. Gain performance insights and metrics that help you manage your exertion and build stamina. Optimize recovery with 24/7 health and wellness monitoring of heart rate, respiration, stress, sleep, and more (this device is intended to give an estimation of your activity and metrics; it is not a medical device). Outdoor navigation sensors and new multi-band GNSS technology help guide you with a higher level of positioning accuracy, even in challenging environments. Plus, you’ll have preloaded TopoActive maps and worldwide ski and golf maps right on your wrist. To complement your tamer days, connected features include smart notifications when connected to a compatible smartphone, music storage, and Garmin Pay contactless payments in supported countries and payment networks.

features: Long-running solar powered multisport GPS watch with scratch-resistant Power Sapphire lens and always-on 1.3-in display uses the sun’s energy to extend battery life,24/7 health and wellness monitoring with wrist-based heart rate, Pulse Ox (not available-inall countries), stress, and enhanced sleep tracking (this device is-inended to give an estimation of your activity and metrics; it is not a medical device),Takes training to the next level with endurance and real-time stamina tracking, training status, advanced performance metrics and 30+ built-in sports apps,Multi-band frequency and GNSS network support (GPS, GLONASS and Galileo) to navigate outdoors with higher level of positioning accuracy plus built-in sensors for 3-axis compass, gyroscope and barometric altimeter,Trusted button controls that work in any environment are matched with a highly responsive touchscreen interface for quick, convenient access to selections,Preloaded TopoActive maps plus maps for thousands of golf courses and ski resorts worldwide,Built-in Wi-Fi connectivity lets user download maps for any continent at any time without using a computer,Access to smart notifications when paired with a compatible smartphone, music storage, and Garmin Pay contactless payment solution in supported countries and payment networks,Battery performance: up to 18 days of battery life while indoors or up to 22 days when solar charging in smartwatch mode; in GPS Mode, up to 57 hours indoors or up to 73 hours when solar charging
name: Garmin fēnix 7 Sapphire Solar Multisport GPS Watch (Black DLC Titanium, Black Band)

description: This Frigidaire 20 cubic foot top freezer refrigerator fits in the same sized cutout as a traditional 18 cu. Ft. Model (30-in width x 66-in height cutout. This refrigerator features the EvenTemp™ cooling system, precise temperature control which keeps food at one ideal temperature. Spacious interior storage options include a full-width deli drawer, generous door bins, and a full-width glass freezer shelf. This Lowe's Exclusive is similar to FFTR2045VS but features EasyCare™ Stainless Steel with an easy-to-clean fingerprint-resistant finish.
descriptionHtml: This Frigidaire 20 cubic foot top freezer refrigerator fits in the same sized cutout as a traditional 18 cu. Ft. Model (30-in width x 66-in height cutout. This refrigerator features the EvenTemp™ cooling system, precise temperature control which keeps food at one ideal temperature. Spacious interior storage options include a full-width deli drawer, generous door bins, and a full-width glass freezer shelf. This Lowe's Exclusive is similar to FFTR2045VS but features EasyCare™ Stainless Steel with an easy-to-clean fingerprint-resistant finish.
features: More capacity, same cutout: Stock up with 20-cu ft of storage that fits standard 18-cu ft fridge cutout,Fingerprint resistant: Lowe's Exclusive EasyCare resists fingerprints and is easy to clean.,Prevent warm spots and unwanted freezing with our EvenTemp cooling system's optimized airflow that ensures a consistent temperature throughout your refrigerator.,Find a place for everything with our spacious interior storage options designed for busy families, including a full-width deli drawer, two glass shelves, generous door bins, and a full-width glass freezer shelf,Keep produce fresher longer, so you waste less and save money with our humidity-controlled crisper drawers with roller support,Avoid spoiled food and soupy ice cream with our auto-close doors, which ensure your doors are never left slightly open by automatically closing once the door is ajar or less,Each refrigerator has gone through a 42-point quality check ensuring strong performance for years to come,Ice maker ready - enjoy the flexibility of later adding an ice maker without sacrificing valuable freezer space thanks to our optional slim ice maker (sold separately - model # IM117000),Garage Ready- Designed to perform in 45F – 110F conditions to ensure optimal performance in a variety of climates
name: Frigidaire Garage-Ready 20-cu ft Top-Freezer Refrigerator (Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel)

description: The V-Series 13PC. 1/2" Drive Metric Deep 6-Point Socket Set delivers unprecendented performance to the Craftsman brand. Engineered for professionals, this socket set features a magnetic socket rail for easy socket storage and organization. The sockets have premium features such as the 6-Point Socket Geometry that maximizes torque onto the flats of fasteners with an off-corner design. Other features include a chamfered and tapered tip design, which provides users with quicker socket-to-fastener engagement.  Backed by Craftsman's Lifetime Warranty, this product is designed to deliver the quality and durability expected from the Craftsman brand. If the product fails to perform for any reason, we will replace it. Return damaged product to a stocking Retail Partner or call 1-888-331-4569 for details. No proof of purchase required.

description: The V-Series 12PC. 3/8" Drive X-Tract™ Technology Hex Bit Socket Set delivers unprecendented performance to the Craftsman brand. Engineered for professionals, this hex bit socket set features Craftsman's newest fastener gripping innovation. X-Tract™ Technology is a bit geometry designed to extract fasteners that are up to 50% rounded without inflicting damage to the fastener. In addition to extraction, this geometry helps prevent future rounding while tightening and loosening fasteners. Therefore, the X-Tract™ Technology hex bit socket is perfect for everyday use and is also an effective extraction solution. Backed by Craftsman's Lifetime Warranty, this product is designed to deliver the quality and durability expected from the Craftsman brand. If the product fails to perform for any reason, we will replace it. Return damaged product to a stocking Retail Partner or call 1-888-331-4569 for details. No proof of purchase required.

description: With today's electric vehicles, a standard wall outlet won't cut it anymore. The ChargePoint Home Flex adds 37 miles of range per hour to your electric vehicle.   The Level 2, 240V home charger delivers up to 50 amps of charging speed, charging your electric car up to 9 times faster than the typical wall outlet. Compatible with any electric car, the ChargePoint Home Flex was tested on leading electric vehicle models, such as the Nissan LEAF, Chevrolet Volts, Tesla cars, and more. Use the ChargePoint app to set calendar reminders, charging schedules, and review your charging data.   The WiFi-enabled EV charging station is compatible with Amazon Alexa devices. Install the home charging station indoors or outdoors. Installation by an electrician is easy. Choose from hardwired or plug-in installation. Plug-in installation with NEMA 14-50 outlet requires circuits rated 40A or 50A. The 23-foot long charging cable easily connects to your Toyota Prius Prime, BMW i3, or other electric vehicle.   Charge up for your commute from your own garage with the ChargePoint Home Flex EV Charger.

description: Experience a Full Body Workout: Enjoy total-body strength training in the comfort of your own home with the NordicTrack Select-a-Weight Dumbbells. With a max weight of 55-pounds each, these versatile dumbbells can replace 30 weights in one compact, easy-to-use set. Easily choose between 10 and 55 pounds with a smooth weight selection system, and enjoy convenient storage in custom-molded trays that are clearly marked with weight identification. Discover iFit Workouts: Download the iFit app and start your free trial to stream on-demand video workouts directly to your own tablet or smartphone. With iFit, professional trainers will coach you through a variety of strength-building workouts on your time, in your home. Replace 30 Dumbbells: Each Select-a-Weight dumbbell features 15 weight selections, so you can move in 5-pound and 2.5-pound increments from 10 to 55 pounds. Replace an entire rack of dumbbells with these compact adjustable weights. Smooth Weight Selection System: Adjust your dumbbells in 2.5 or 5-pound increments to dial in the best weight for a variety of strength-building exercises in the comfort of your own home gym - simply lift and push the Select-a-Weight tab to easily modify your dumbbell. Fitted Storage Trays Included: When not in use, your NordicTrack adjustable dumbbells can be securely stored in custom-molded trays that are clearly marked with weight identification.

description: Versatile & Portable Rolling Storage Cart - Convenient Organization for Any Space  Transform your organization game with this versatile rolling storage cart from the Network Collection. This lightweight storage solution is perfect for decluttering and organizing a wide range of items, from office supplies and pantry items to clothing and toiletries.  Featuring six removable drawers, this cart offers ample storage space to accommodate various-sized items, from small notepads and note cards to crafts and accessories. The completely removable drawers provide easy access to your belongings whenever you need them.  Thanks to the omnidirectional wheels, you can effortlessly move the cart from room to room as your needs change. The wheel locks ensure stability and safety when the cart is stationary, keeping your items securely in place.  The see-through mesh design of this vertical storage solution makes it easy to locate and organize multiple items. With its seamless black color, the cart also serves as a stylish home décor element. Ideal for any home or office, our storage cart makes a thoughtful gift for graduations, housewarming parties, holidays, and other special occasions.  Experience the convenience and flexibility of the Versatile & Portable Rolling Storage Cart, and bring order to any space in your home or office.

description: The YTX14 AHGEL is a 12-Volt 12 Ah GEL (maintenance free) battery. Requires no addition of water during the life of the battery. The MIGHTY MAX YTX 14 Ah GEL is a true deep cycle battery that can be mounted in any position, requires no maintenance. When a GEL cell battery is charged, no hazardous fumes escape the battery case, gases are processed within the battery itself. Common uses for the YTX14 Ah GEL: ATVs, Motorcycles, personal watercraft, jet ski's, snowmobiles and more.

description: Elevate your entire work space to think on your feet with this L-shaped standing desk from Hanover. A push of a button is all you need to take your desk from sit to stand with motorized height adjustments with 3 programmable memory presets. Three legs and a 90 degree bend make this desktop perfect for placement in a corner or in the middle of a room as a makeshift divider. With ample room and weight capacity to support multiple computer monitors as well as other devices and important documents, there's plenty of room for work and leisure activities like crafting or gaming! Extended sitting puts more strain on your body than you may think, so give your standing muscles some exercise with Hanover's standing desk series.

description: The MIND READER Rolling File Cabinet brings you sleek, space-saving, mobile storage for your kitchen, garage, basement, or office. Featuring three smooth-gliding drawers with cut out handles, that can be pulled all the way out, removed, reorganized, and restored snugly as many times as you like Our mesh drawer organizer is lightweight, even when filled, making maneuvering and gliding it around your home on its four caster wheels a breeze. It's perfect for all kinds of items like paper, tools, toys, and all other things your family can think of. The two tall storage drawers and three slim trays give you endless storage possibilities. Other rolling drawer organizer carts are built with flimsy materials, easily bending, warping, or breaking under the weight of your things. The mesh metal frame on our rolling cart organizer has been precision engineered for strength and durability. The MIND READER Rolling File Cabinet is made with a combination of top-grade plastic and steel, ensuring durable storage that will keep your items neatly stored for as long as you need. The drawers are also removable and make cleaning this slim storage cart effortless. Whether it's kitchen spills, makeup stains, or paint from the garage or tool shed, just quickly wipe it using a dry or wet cloth, and your rolling toolbox with drawers will be looking fresh and new! The MIND READER Rolling File Cabinet is your all in one solution for your storage and organizing needs. Buy one today!

description: The YTX16-BS GEL is a 12-Volt 14 Ah GEL (maintenance free) battery. Requires no addition of water during the life of the battery. The MIGHTY MAX YTX16-BS GEL is a true deep cycle battery that can be mounted in any position, requires no maintenance. When a GEL cell battery is charged, no hazardous fumes escape the battery case, gases are processed within the battery itself. Common uses for the YTX16-BS GEL: ATVs, Motorcycles, personal watercraft, jet ski's, snowmobiles and more.

description: Effortlessly Organize Your Space with this Rolling Cabinet This sleek and modern rolling cabinet is a versatile storage solution that offers convenience and style to any home or office. Its minimalist design allows it to blend in seamlessly with any decor, while its compact size and rolling wheels make it easy to move around and store in tight spaces.  With three spacious drawers, this file cabinet offers ample storage space for all your office supplies, documents, craft materials, or personal items. The drawers are made from sturdy mesh material, making it easy to see what's inside, while ensuring that your items are properly ventilated. The smooth gliding drawers make it effortless to access your items quickly and easily. An attractive wooden top adds style and provides a stable functioning surface for sorting files or additional storage.  Built to last, this file cabinet is made from high-quality metal, which can withstand daily use. The sturdy frame and strong mesh drawers ensure that your items are safe and secure, while the easy-to-clean surface makes it simple to maintain and keep looking like new.  Measuring 14.25 inches long by 10.75 inches wide by 25 inches tall (36.19 x 27.31 x 63.5 cm) and weighing just 10.78 lbs (4.89 kgs), this file cabinet can fit snugly under a desk, in a closet, or even in a corner of your room. It's the perfect gift for anyone who values simplicity and organization, whether they're a college student, a work-from-home employee, or anyone looking to keep their space tidy and clutter-free.  Invest in this rolling cabinet from the Network Collection today and discover the convenience and style it brings to your life.

description: The YTX24HL-BS GEL is a 12-Volt 21 Ah GEL (maintenance free) battery. Requires no addition of water during the life of the battery. The MIGHTY MAX YTX24HL-BS GEL is a true deep cycle battery that can be mounted in any position, requires no maintenance. When a GEL cell battery is charged, no hazardous fumes escape the battery case, gases are processed within the battery itself. Common uses for the YTX24HL-BS GEL: ATVs, Motorcycles, personal watercraft, jet ski's, snowmobiles and more.

features: YTX24HL-BSGEL is a 12-Volt 21 Ah 350 Cold Cranking Amps (CCA) GEL (maintenance free) battery,Factory activated GEL battery, maintenance free, no acid pack needed, advanced design works right out of the box and requires no maintenance yet offers the option to prolong the standard life by adding extra electrolytes,True deep cycle battery that can be mounted in any position, resists shocks and vibration, long-lasting high performance in high and low temperatures,Environment friendly, leaving no pollution to the environment while charging and discharging, zero fumes or chemicals escape the battery casing, all chemical reactions are done within the battery itself,Dimensions: 8.07 in. x 3.42 in. x 6.37 in. polarity: negative on left, positive on right, listing is for the battery and screws only, no wire harness or mounting accessories included
name: Mighty Max Battery YTX24HL-BSGEL 12V 21Ah 350 CCA GEL ATV Battery - Maintenance-Free, Factory Activated, Deep Cycle, Resistant to Shocks and Vibration

description: Take your storage solutions to the next level with a Mind Reader MDF Multi-tier Printer Cart. Elevate your storage solutions with this uniquely styled rolling supply cart. Designed to hold substantial supplies without allowing them to spill or fall over the sides, the sturdy sections on each level provide ample storage space while allowing you to still view the contents clearly. Say goodbye to tacky plastic storage units, and replace them with a rolling cart that’s built to last. The unobtrusive design blends in seamlessly at home, at the office, or even in the classroom. The 360° omnidirectional casters at the bottom provide a full range of motion, so you can comfortably wheel this cart around, even navigating tight corners with ease. The cart itself is constructed from premium MDF, with enough clearance to allow for storage and transportation of ink, paper, toner, cables, office supplies, hair products, fitness gear, or anything else you might need to store. The raised sides of the storage baskets ensure that your charcuterie won’t spill across the floor in transit. Take printing on a roll with this storage cart from Mind Reader products. Dimensions: 11.81″ L x 15.75″ W x 13.78″ H. Weight Capacity: 70 lbs. (31.75 kg). Materials: MDF.

description: Bring all the tools you need to get in shape right in the comfort of your home with the TRX2500. The powerful XTERRA 2.25 HP motor provides speeds up to 10 mph. Users can also vary the large 20in x 55in belt to incline levels from 0-10 for maximum workout variety.   The console display features an easy to read large 5.5in Blue Backlit LCD display with 24 preset programs for users of all fitness levels. Other convenient features include the direct access speed and incline buttons for quick workout changes, convenient handlebar controls for both speed and incline, speakers for your favorite tunes, and a cooling fan to keep you cool.  When not in use you can fold up the treadmill with the Lift Assist frame design, which also includes a Safe Drop feature that slowly lowers the deck for added safety. Built as tough as the ultimate race it is named after, this XTERRA treadmill delivers performance and results.

description: Effortlessly Organize Your Space with this Rolling File Cabinet This sleek and modern rolling cabinet is a versatile storage solution that offers convenience and style to any home or office. Its minimalist design allows it to blend in seamlessly with any decor, while its compact size and rolling wheels make it easy to move around and store in tight spaces.  With three spacious drawers, this file cabinet offers ample storage space for all your office supplies, documents, craft materials, or personal items. The drawers are made from sturdy mesh material, making it easy to see what's inside, while ensuring that your items are properly ventilated. Plus, the smooth gliding drawers make it effortless to access your items quickly and easily.  Built to last, this file cabinet is made from high-quality metal, which can withstand daily use. The sturdy frame and strong mesh drawers ensure that your items are safe and secure, while the easy-to-clean surface makes it simple to maintain and keep looking like new.  Measuring 12.5 inches long by 13 inches wide by 25 inches tall (31.75 x 33.02 x 63.5 cm) and weighing just 6.3 lbs (2.9 kgs), this file cabinet can fit snugly under a desk, in a closet, or even in a corner of your room. It's the perfect gift for anyone who values simplicity and organization, whether they're a college student, a work-from-home employee, or anyone looking to keep their space tidy and clutter-free.  Invest in this rolling file cabinet from the Network Collection today and discover the convenience and style it brings to your life.

description: Professional Cycling Training at Home: Enjoy low-impact exercise that is customized to your exact needs on the NordicTrack Commercial R 35 Recumbent exercise bike. Stream live and on-demand iFIT workouts directly through your stationary bike’s 14” touchscreen, following your favorite trainers through exciting Global Workouts and Studio Classes. With an included 30-day iFIT membership, this bike delivers everything you need for exceptional home exercise. 30-Day iFIT Family Membership Included: The NordicTrack Commercial R 35 includes a 30-day iFIT family membership that lets you create up to 5 individual profiles that each track health metrics, workout history, and exercise preferences. Immersive 14” Smart HD Touchscreen: Browse the expansive iFIT Library and stream live and on-demand workouts right on your indoor bike’s 14” smart HD touchscreen. Automatic Trainer Control: With iFIT, your trainers will auto-adjust your resistance to match global terrains and optimize every workout to help you meet your fitness goals. Stream Live & On-Demand Workouts: Choose from thousands of on-demand workouts filmed around the world and in the studio, or visit the ‘On-Air’ section to view upcoming live events and classes.

description: UltraShield Naturale outdoor composite deck tiles by NewTechWood. We are proud to introduce our newest line of deck tiles the Naturale line. We have outfitted these deck tiles with the most realistic looking composite on the market today. The Naturale embossing gives these deck tiles that exotic wood look. These tiles are a quick and easy fix for covering up that old cracked or unsightly concrete patio or balcony. These deck tiles snap together in a flash and they allow rain water to run through. Made from high density recycled plastic composite material, they are the perfect solution for that roof top patio or deck. Additionally they're manufactured using our proven UltraShield technology, which encapsulates the core material with a Multichromatic poly shell to protect it from the elements. Best of all, if you move, simply unsnap them apart and take them with you. Ultra-low maintenance, ultra-durable, ultra-beautiful.

description: Get the most out of your décor and workspace with the Allen + Roth Mid-Century Modern Adjustable Writing Desk! Styled to perfection, this charming desk features 2 front drawers to store anything from homework assignments to legal documents with ease from the pull-out knobs located on each drawer and the soft close drawer glides. You can also adjust the levelers on the legs to accommodate your height. The ample space atop the surface gives plenty of room for your laptop and papers as well as desk accessories; such as, pencil holders, document trays, paperclips, post-it notes and even a nice, small desk lamp to add extra lighting. Place The Allen + Roth Mid-Century Modern Adjustable Writing Desk in your home office, study or dorm room to enjoy a pleasurable study-time environment. Constructed of particle board, paper veneer and rubberwood legs for durability and extended use. Measures 31.5"H x 43.5"W x 19D.

description: The YTX24HL-BS GEL is a 12-Volt 21 Ah GEL (maintenance free) battery. Requires no addition of water during the life of the battery. The MIGHTY MAX YTX24HL-BS GEL is a true deep cycle battery that can be mounted in any position, requires no maintenance. When a GEL cell battery is charged, no hazardous fumes escape the battery case, gases are processed within the battery itself. Common uses for the YTX24HL-BS GEL: ATVs, Motorcycles, personal watercraft, jet ski's, snowmobiles and more.

description: Effortlessly Organize Your Space with this 4 Drawer Cabinet This sleek and modern cabinet is a versatile storage solution that offers convenience and style to any home or office. Its minimalist design allows it to blend in seamlessly with any decor, while its compact size and Lightweight make it easy to move around.  With four spacious drawers, this cabinet offers ample storage space for all your office supplies, documents, craft materials, or personal items. The drawers are made from sturdy mesh material, making it easy to see what's inside, while ensuring that your items are properly ventilated. The smooth gliding drawers make it effortless to access your items quickly and easily.   Built to last, this file cabinet is made from high-quality metal, which can withstand daily use. The sturdy frame and strong mesh drawers ensure that your items are safe and secure, while the easy-to-clean surface makes it simple to maintain and keep looking like new.  Measuring 10.2 inches long by 12.6 inches wide by 15.6 inches tall (25.91 x 32 x 39.62 cm) and weighing just 6.38 lbs (2.89 kgs), this cabinet can fit snugly on a desk, in a closet, or cabinet. It's the perfect gift for anyone who values simplicity and organization, whether they're a college student, a work-from-home employee, or anyone looking to keep their space tidy and clutter-free.  Invest in this cabinet from the Network Collection today and discover the convenience and style it brings to your life.

description: This Frigidaire Gallery French door refrigerator maintains the taste and texture of even your most delicate foods. Lettuce and broccoli stay fresh and crisp for longer in our exclusive CrispSeal® fresh crispers than in any comparable crispers. Our 3 advanced technologies block out dry air, automatically optimize humidity while removing excess moisture, and our built-in antioxidant filter reduces ethylene gas, odors and preserves produce color. Get more storage out of your refrigerator with clever organization solutions that maximize usable space, including in-door condiment storage, a slide-under shelf, a snack zone, a flexible bin which can be used as crisper or an open compartment, and accessory railing system which works with our optional storage pan and wine rack. Get extra space for all your most used items with the custom-flex temp drawer. Store yogurt, beer, or even frozen pizzas with the middle drawer that can be a refrigerator or a freezer.

description: When it comes to choosing materials for your indoor or outdoor projects, one truth reigns above all else: there’s nothing like the real thing. Redwood’s beauty and strength come from natural qualities inherent in this majestic specie of wood. It has long been the building material of choice for interior accents because of it’s one-of-a-kind look, and for outdoor living projects due to its legendary durability. Redwood’s tannins give the lumber warm tones and exemplary strength against insects and moisture, proving its durability time and time again for more than a century. Redwood is a renewable resource and environmentally responsible choice for projects inside and out. The redwood in Lowe's is harvested from family owned forestlands along California's coast, where trees grow slowly and develop the strength, warm tones and natural durability inherent in this specie of lumber. Fine-milled close to the source, every bit of the resource is utilized – right down to the bark and sawdust that go into making great garden mulch and soil amendments. There are no landfill issues with redwood either because redwood is recyclable and entirely biodegradable. That’s all part of why building with redwood goes hand-in-hand with living sustainable.
